20I%20started%20networking%20on%20LinkedIn%20in%20the%20early%20days%20of%202016%20and%20talked%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20at%20companies%20like%20Meta%20through%20LinkedIn%20InMail%20and%20personal%20invites.%20I%20also%20went%20to%20career%20fairs%20and%20networking%20events%2C%20where%20I%20connected%20with%20people%20on%20LinkedIn%20ahead%20of%20time%20%E2%80%94%20this%20approach%20helped%20me%20stand%20out%20and%20ensured%20that%20I%20wouldn't%20get%20lost%20in%20the%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinkedin-message-college-student-job-snapchat-recruiter-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20landed%20my%20first%20job%20at%20Snapchat%20through%20LinkedIn%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20in%20the%20search%20bar%2C%20I%20typed%20in%20%26quot%3Bhiring%20manager%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Boperations.%26quot%3B%20I%20found%20a%20recruiter%20at%20Snap%20and%20I%20sent%20her%20a%20personalized%20invite%20to%20connect%20with%20her.%20At%20first%2C%20she%20didn't%20respond%2C%20so%20I%20sent%20another%20message%20with%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20months%20later%2C%20she%20said%20that%20there%20was%20an%20operation%20specialist%20role%20available.%20Then%20I%20got%20the%20interviews.%20During%20the%20interview%2C%20I%20also%20prepared%20a%20case%20study.%20I%20put%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwonsulting-resume-snapchat-job-right-out-of-college-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emy%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20business%20project%20tailored%20towards%20the%20job%20description%20in%20a%20yellow%20folder%20(because%20yellow%20is%20Snapchat's%20color)%20and%20gave%20it%20to%20them.%20Two%20hours%20later%2C%20I%20got%20the%20offer%20from%20Snapchat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20much%20money%20I%20made%20working%20in%20tech%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESnap%3A%20Product