20%E2%80%94%20but%20efficient%20%E2%80%94%20interview%20tip%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShowcasing%20your%20relevant%20skills%20and%20experience%20is%20crucial%20during%20interviews.%20I%20always%20look%20at%20the%20job%20description%20and%20preemptively%20include%20an%20anecdote%20that%20addresses%20the%20%26quot%3BTell%20me%20about%20a%20time%20when%E2%80%A6%26quot%3B%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20responsibility%20in%20the%20job%20description%20could%20be%20%26quot%3Bcollaborate%20with%20a%20sales%20team%20to%20figure%20out%20problems.%26quot%3B%20In%20my%20mind%2C%20I%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20question%3A%20%26quot%3BTell%20me%20about%20a%20time%20when%20you%20worked%20with%20sales%20teams%20to%20figure%20out%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20I%20share%20a%20specific%20situation%20of%20when%20I%20did%20that%20in%20my%20past%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20way%2C%20I%20know%20the%20whole%20job%20description%20from%20top%20to%20bottom%20and%20exactly%20how%20my%20past%20experiences%20match%20the%20responsibilites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20need%20to%20build%20your%20network%20early%20on%20to%20land%20your%20dream%20job%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBuilding%20your%20network%20early%20on%20makes%20a%20big%20difference%20in%20job%20hunting.%20Before%20negotiating%20compensation%2C%20I%20asked%20peers%20who%20worked%20at%20other%20tech%20companies%20what%20a%20reasonable%20pay%20range%20might%20be.%20With%20that%20information%2C%20I%20felt%20much%20more%20confident%20during%20interviews.%20It's%20better%20than%20relying%20solely%20on%20websites%20like%20Glassdoor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20after%20building%20the%20relationship%2C%20I%20felt%20more%20comfortable%20asking%20them%20if%20my%20total%20compensation%C2%A0was%20reasonable%20for%20the%20experience%20that%20I%20had.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20usually%20happens%20is%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20folks%20get%20the%20job%20first%2C%20and%20then%20start%20asking%20around.%20But%20no