r-old%2C%20that's%20amazing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20loved%20the%20casual%20paradise.%20It%20was%20the%20antithesis%20of%20life%20in%20Sydney%2C%20where%20they%20lived%20full%20time.%20For%20the%20next%2013%20years%20a%20local%20family%20ran%20their%20caf%C3%A9%20and%20another%20resident%20managed%20the%20holiday%20huts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20after%20Michael%20Maxwell%20retired%20and%20Timmy%20Maxwell%20gained%20experience%20working%20in%20hospitality%2C%20the%20father%20and%20son%20decided%20to%20make%20Lord%20Howe%20Island%20their%20permanent%20home%20and%20rebuild%20the%20huts%20to%20rent%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStarting%20renovations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20bought%20the%20rights%20to%20a%20plant%20nursery%20next%20to%20their%20property.%20They%20also%20decided%20to%20turn%20the%20caf%C3%A9%20and%20the%20holiday%20huts%20into%20a%20new%20family%20home%20for%20themselves%20and%20build%20two%20new%20holiday%20houses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20brown%20house%20being%20built%20in%20a%20jungle%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c7e372cf0778001967ba41%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERenovations%20underway.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Island%20House%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20neither%20had%20worked%20in%20home%20development%2C%20the%20father%20and%20son%20said%20they%20weren't%20intimidated%20by%20the%20challenge.%20Timmy%20Maxwell%20joked%20that%20his%20father%20was%20always%20knocking%20down%20walls%20in%20the%20homes%20they'd%20lived%20in.%20%26quot%3BEver%20since%20I%20was%20a%20toddler%20there%20were%20always%20paint%20tins%20or%20new%20pieces%20of%20furniture%20being%20shuffled%20around%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20wanted%20the%20new%20buildings%20to%20be%20more%20striking%20than%20the%20holiday%20huts%20they'd%20removed%2C%20but%20also%20to%20disappear%20into%20the%20surroundings.%20The%20architects%20they%20commissioned%20mapped%20the%20position%20of%20the%20trees%20on%20the%20grounds%2C%20then%20created%20raised%20villas%20around%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20inside%20of%20a%20house%20being%20renovated%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c7e3accf0778001967baa9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInterior%20renovations.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Island%20House%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20timber%20and%20copper%20used%20in%20the%20building%20were%20designed%20to%20help%20the%20houses'%20exteriors%20age%20well%20and%20blend%20into%20the%20landscape.%20Sustainable%20development%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lhib.nsw.gov.au%2Finfrastructure%2Felectricity%23%3A~%3Atext%3DElectricity%2520on%2520the%2520Island%2520is%2CSeries%252060%2520diesel%2520generating%2520units%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eencouraged%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20island%2C%20so%20the%20Maxwells%20made%20use%20of%20solar%20power%20and%20rainwater%20throughout%20the%20property.%20They%20also%20oriented%20the%20villas%20so%20guests%20could%20wake%20up%20to%20views%20of%20the%20jungle%20filled%20with%20800-year-old%20banyan%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20copper%20bathtub%20outside%20on%20a%20patio%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c7e55bcf0778001967bd5d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224066%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20outdoor%20copper%20bathtub%20in%20the%20North%20House.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Island%20House%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFacing%20challenges%20and%20sourcing%20furniture%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Maxwells%20realized%20that%20building%20new%20homes%20on%