2%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b1991a9751e300192a2c10%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222232%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMark%20Zuckerberg.%3Cp%3EJeff%20Bottari%2FZuffa%20LLC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMeta's%20move%20away%20from%20its%20former%20Facebook%20name%20came%20amid%20new%20wave%20of%20controversy%20for%20the%20company.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Bridiculous%26quot%3B%20to%20connect%20a%20new%20name%20to%20ongoing%20%26quot%3BFacebook%20Papers%26quot%3B%20coverage.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EYet%2C%20executive%20Chris%20Cox%20did%20just%20that%20when%20asked%20by%20an%20employee%20about%20the%20success%20of%20the%20new%20name.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Facebook%20first%20revealed%20it%20was%20renaming%20itself%20Meta%20in%20October%202021%2C%20the%20company%20said%20it%20was%20about%20nothing%20more%20than%20a%20new%20desire%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bmetaverse%20first.%26quot%3B%20It%20didn't%20take%20long%20for%20a%20top%20executive%20to%20revel%20in%20the%20new%20name%20elbowing%20out%20bad%20press.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20to%20Meta%20came%20about%20three%20weeks%20after%20whistleblower%20Frances%20Haugen%20went%20public%20on%2060%20Minutes%20as%20the%20person%20behind%20the%20disclosures%20being%20reported%20on%20at%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%2C%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3BFacebook%20Papers%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-papers-mark-zuckerberg-frances-haugen-leaked-docs-2021-10%5C%22%3Erevelations%20from%20which%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20being%20covered%20by%20the%20press%20globally.%20Given%20widespread%20speculation%20that%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20name%20change%20was%20related%20to%20the%20whistleblower%20disclosures%2C%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%2C%20whose%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-mark-zuckerberg-meta-facebook-ceo-layoffs-profit-cage-match-2023-7%5C%22%3Erecent%20executive%20transformation%20was%20reported%20on%20by%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20such%20a%20connection%20was%20%26quot%3Bridiculous.%26quot%3B%20His%20chief%20product%20officer%20Chris%20Cox%20easily%20connected%20the%20two%20about%20two%20weeks%20later%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-mark-zuckerberg-meta-facebook-ceo-layoffs-profit-cage-match-2023-7%5C%22%3EInsider's%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20company-wide%20Q%26amp%3BA%20with%20employees%20in%20November%202021%2C%20led%20by%20Cox%20and%20Sheryl%20Sandberg%2C%20then%20Meta's%20chief%20operations%20officer%2C%20an%20employee%20asked%20about%20the%20overall%20success%20of%20the%20new%20Meta%20name%2C%20a%20longtime%20employee%20who%20has%20since%20left%20the%20company%20recalled.%20Cox%20said%20the%20name%20change%20was%20successful%2C%20explaining%20his%20measure%20of%20success%20was%20the%20amount%20of%20press%20coverage%20of%20the%20name%20change%20compared%20to%20the%20whistleblower%20disclosures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20more%20than%20double%20the%20volume%20of%20the%20Facebook%20Papers%20coverage%2C%26quot%3B%20Cox%20said%20on%20the%20call.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20coverage%20was%20also%20%26quot%3Bneutral%20to%20positive%20in%20tone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20kind%20of%20thing%20that%20we%20only%20could%20have%20dreamed%20of%20when%20we%20did%20the%20change%20in%20terms%20of%20press%20coverage%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20went%20on.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it%20was%20a%20really%20big%20deal%20because%20Facebook%20Papers%20was%20a%20big%20story%2C%20especially%20inside%20the%20US.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Cox's%20focus%20on%20the%20comparison%20was%20the%20volume%20of%20press%20coverage%2C%20the%20former%20employee%20who%20was%20present%20for%20the%20call%20was%20surprised%20by%20the%20answer.%20The%20person%20told%20Insider%20they%20and%20other%20colleagues%20at%20the%20time%20took%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20bald%20statement%20that%20the%20name%20change%20was%20meant%20to%20move%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20press.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Zuckerberg's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-metaverse-losses-top-40-billion-suddenly-ok-meta-2023-7%5C%22%3Emulti-billion%20metaverse%20push%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20yet%20to%20become%20a%20financial%20plus%20for%20Meta%2C%20the%20rename%20drove%20months%20of%20coverage%20around%20the%20metaverse%2C%20and%20the%20new%20name%20has%20stuck%20with%20the%20media.%20As%20Eric%20Schiffer%2C%20CEO%20of%20private%20equity%20firm%20The%20Patriarch%20Organization%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-metaverse-new-name-change-could-save-it-2021-10%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20name%20change%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20absolutely%20a%20genius%20move%20to%20shift%20away%2C%20to%20rebrand%20to%20the%20metaverse%2C%20and%20wash%20away%20the%20past%20pain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20Meta%20employee%20or%20someone%20else%20with%20insight%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20Kali%20Hays%20at%20khays%40insider.com%2C%20on%20secure%20messaging%20app%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsignal.org%2Fdownload%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cem%3ESignal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20at%20949-280-0267%2C%20or%20through%20Twitter%20DM%20at%20%40hayskali.%20Reach%20out%20using%20a%20non-work%20device.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-exec-said-rebrand-succeeded-in-beating-facebook-papers-coverage-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690880401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-exec-said-rebrand-succeeded-in-beating-facebook-papers-coverage