toxicated%20once%20again%20stopped%20our%20car.%20This%20group%20appeared%20to%20be%20diligently%20checking%20every%20vehicle%20passing%20through%20the%20Kuki-dominated%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ETreatment%20towards%20vehicles%20differ%20depending%20on%20whether%20you%20are%20traveling%20to%20or%20from%20the%20hills.%20Meiteis%20in%20the%20valley%20inspect%20cars%20coming%20from%20the%20hills%C2%A0while%20Kukis%20scrutinise%20vehicles%20headed%20towards%20the%20hills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAs%20we%20approached%20the%20area%20of%20Terakhongshangbi%2C%20our%20car%20was%20stopped%20by%20a%20few%20locals%20who%20urgently%20requested%20that%20we%20turn%20off%20our%20lights%20as%20firing%20was%20taking%20place%20in%20the%20vicinity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAround%2020%20women%20were%20sitting%20in%20a%20small%20cottage.%20They%20told%20The%20Wire%20that%20they%20were%20Meira%20Paibis.%20One%20woman%20who%20identified%20her%20as%20Sanahanbi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20government%20started%20ruling%20the%20state%2C%20we%20thought%20that%20all%20our%20miseries%20and%20grievances%20would%20be%20heard.%20But%20this%20didn%E2%80%99t%20happen.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESanahanbi%20said%20that%20she%20would%20still%20appeal%20to%20Biren%20to%20solve%20the%20present%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAs%20the%20sound%20of%20guns%20continued%2C%20the%20Meira%20Paibis%20in%20the%20cottage%20turned%20off%20the%20lights.%20Another%20woman%2C%20who%20identified%20herself%20as%20Sanatombi%2C%20questioned%20the%20government%20for%20still%20banning%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20internet%20services.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20Meitei%20people%20were%20given%20access%20to%20internet%2C%20more%20stories%20of%20suffering%20would%20come%20to%20be%20known.%20A%20month%20ago%2C%20police%20promised%20to%20provide%20protection%