event%20organised%20by%20the%20Lokmanya%20Tilak%20Smarak%20Mandir%20Trust%2C%20where%20PM%20Modi%20received%20the%20Lokmanya%20Tilak%20National%20Award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20on%20stage%20were%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20his%20Deputy%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20rebel%20nephew%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20who%20split%20the%20NCP%20recently%20and%20joined%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP.%20PM%20Modi%20also%20greeted%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20giving%20him%20a%20pat%20on%20the%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20speech%20peppered%20with%20Marathi%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20development%20was%20impossible%20in%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20mistrust.%20%26quot%3BTrust%20in%20each%20other%20will%20make%20us%20strong%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20On%20freedom%20icon%20Bal%20Gangadhar%20Tilak%2C%20or%20Lokmanya%20Tilak%2C%20the%20PM%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BLokmanya%20Tilak%20had%20this%20unique%20ability%20to%20identify%20young%20talent.%20Veer%20Savarkar%20was%20one%20such%20example.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BLokmanya%20Tilak%20wanted%20to%20get%20total%20freedom%20for%20the%20country%20and%20he%20spent%20his%20early%20days%20in%20Pune.%20To%20be%20independent%20from%20the%20British%2C%20Tilak%20knew%20he%20needed%20to%20unite%20the%20masses.%20He%20became%20a%20journalist%20and%20then%20had%20Kesari%20and%20Maratha%20weekly%20newspapers%20and%20fought%20against%20the%20British.%20Tilak%20used%20to%20say%20there%20shouldn't%20be%20any%20pressure%20on%20journalism%20and%20journalists%20shouldn't%20be%20pressured.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar%20last%20appeared%20on%20a%20stage%20together%20seven%20years%20ago.%20As%20his%20Maharashtra%20allies%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20urged%20him%20to%20skip%20today's%20event%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20said%20he%20couldn't%20possibly%20beg%20off%2C%20given%20that%20he%20had%20invited%2