0%20C%20Threat%2C%20New%20IPCC%20Head%20Says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01111610%2FProfessor_Jim_Skea.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20newly%20appointed%20head%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fwhat-is-the-ipcc-and-what-does-it-do%2Fa-50552119%5C%22%3Ethe%20UN%E2%80%99s%20Intergovernmental%20Panel%20on%20Climate%20Change%20(IPCC)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Jim%20Skea%2C%20spoke%20to%20two%20major%20German%20news%20outlets%20over%20the%20weekend%2C%20soon%20after%20his%20appointment%20to%20the%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20weekly%20magazine%20%3Cem%3EDer%20Spiegel%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20first%20published%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Skea%20warned%20against%20laying%20too%20much%20value%20on%20the%20international%20community%E2%80%99s%20current%20nominal%20target%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fglobal-warming-world-has-50-50-chance-of-hitting-15c-mark-soon%2Fa-61743456%5C%22%3Elimiting%20global%20warming%20to%201.5%C2%B0%20Celsius%20compared%20the%20pre-industrial%20era%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20should%20not%20despair%20and%20fall%20into%20a%20state%20of%20shock%E2%80%9D%20if%20global%20temperatures%20were%20to%20increase%20by%20this%20amount%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20discussion%20with%20German%20news%20agency%20DPA%2C%20Skea%20expanded%20on%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20constantly%20communicate%20the%20message%20that%20we%20are%20all%20doomed%20to%20extinction%2C%20then%20that%20paralyses%20people%20and%20prevents%20them%20from%20taking%20the%20necessary%20steps%20to%20get%20a%20grip%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fclimate-change%2Ft-18614374%5C%22%3Eclimate%20change%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20world%20won%E2%80%99t%20end%20if%20it%20warms%20by%20more%20than%201.5%C2%B0%2C%E2%80%9D%20Skea%20told%20%3Cem%3EDer%C2%A0Spiegel%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20will%20however%20be%20a%20more%20dangerous%20world.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurpassing%20that%20mark%C2%A0would%20lead%20to%20many%20problems%20and%20social%20tensions%2C%20he%20said%2C%20but%20still%20that%20would%20not%20constitute%20an%20existential%20threat%20to%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20international%20community%E2%80%99s%20stated%20target%20is%20currently%20to%20limit%20global%20warming%20to%20the%201.5%20degrees%20Celsius%20target%2C%20even%20though%20UN%20estimates%20suggest%20that%20the%20current%20commitments%20made%20by%20countries%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fun-report-drives-home-insufficient-global-climate-action%2Fa-65032592%5C%22%3Eare%20actually%20likely%20to%20fall%20far%20short%20of%20their%20nominal%20goal%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20estimates%20that%20within%20roughly%20a%20decade%2C%20the%20target%20is%20liable%20to%20be%20breached.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20else%20did%20Skea%20say%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJames%20%E2%80%9CJim%E2%80%9D%20Skea%20is%20a%20physics%20graduate%20born%20in%20Dundee%20in%20Scotland%20who%20did%20his%20doctoral%20thesis%20in%20energy%20research%20and%20has%20worked%20at%20Imperial%20College%20London%20since%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2069-year-old%2C%20who%20has%20been%20involved%20with%20the%20IPCC%20since%20its%20foundation%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20was%20named%20its%20new%20chairman%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20%3Cem%3EDer%C2%A0Spiegel%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20there%20remained%20good%20reasons%20to%20be%20optimistic%20in%20the%20battle%20against%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20measure%20we%20take%20to%20weaken%20climate%20change%20helps%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20measures%20were%20also%20becoming%20%E2%80%9Cever%20more%20cost-effective.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESkea%20said%20that%20one%20short-term%20focus%20should%20remain%20expanding%20renewable%20electricity%20to%20reduce%20emissions%20from%20fossil%20fuel%20electricity%20generation%20and%20from%20internal%20combustion%20engine%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLonger%20term%2C%20we%20probably%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20do%20without%20technological%20solutions%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fcarbon-capture-storage-explained%2Fa-65624021%5C%22%3Elike%20the%20underground%20capture%20of%20CO2%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20greenhouse%20gas%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fco2-reduction%2Ft-50781286%5C%22%3Ecarbon%20dioxide.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndividual%20abstinence%20is%20good%2C%20but%20new%20infrastructure%20required%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESkea%20predicted%20that%20one%20difficult%20area%20might%20prove%20to%20be%20changing%20people%E2%80%99s%20lifestyles.%20He%20said%20that%20no%20scientist%20could%20tell%20people%20how%20to%20live%20or%20what%20to%20eat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndividual%20abstinence%20is%20good%2C%20but%20it%20alone%20will%20not%20bring%20about%20the%20change%20to%20the%20extent%20it%20will%20be%20necessary%2C%E2%80%9D%20Skea%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20are%20to%20live%20more%20climate%20consciously%2C%20we%20need%20entirely%20new%20infrastructure.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fberlin-environment-blog-cycling-in-berlin-for-the-first-time%2Fa-39788088%5C%22%3EPeople%20will%20not%20get%20on%20bikes%20if%20there%20are%20no%20cycle%20paths%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESkea%20said%20he%20also%20wanted%20to%20adapt%20the%20IPCC%20so%20that%20it%20could%20provide%20better%20and%20more%20targeted%20advice%20to%20specific%20groups%20of%20people%20on%20how%20they%20could%C2%A0act%20to%20combat%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20named%20groups%20like%20town%20planners%2C%20landowners%20and%20businesses%3A%20%E2%80%9CWith%20all%20these%20things%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20real%20people%20and%20their%20real%20lives%2C%20not%20scientific%20abstractions.%20We%20need%20to%20come%20down%20a%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20DPA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20also%20hoped%20to%20make%20progress%20during%20his%20tenure%20on%20how%20and%20where%20money%20was%20sent%20and%20spent%20to%20tackle%20the%20problem%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20enough%20money%20in%20the%20world%2C%20the%20challenge%20is%20getting%20it%20to%20flow%20to%20the%20right%20places%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fclimate-change-do-not-overstate-15-degrees-threat%2Fa-66386523%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690875656000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01111610%2FProfessor_Jim_Skea.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fdont-overstate-1-5-c-threat-new-ipcc-head-says%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jim%20Skea%2C%20the%20new%20head%20of%20the%20UN's%20IPCC%2C%20said%20it's%20not%20helpful%20to%20imply%20that%20a%20temperature%20rise%20of%201.5%C2%B0%20Celsius%20is%20an%20existential%20threat%20to%20humanity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fdont-overstate-1-5-c-threat-new-ipcc-head-says%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ED%20conducts%20raids%20against%20HeroMotors%20Pawan%20Munjal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690875237000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102304419%2Cimgsize-7528.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fmoney-laundering-probe-ed-conducts-raids-against-hero-motocorp-ex