urney%20in%20films%E2%80%8B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fmrunal-thakurs-glorious-journey-in-films%2Fphotostory%2F102300962.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20Why%20UK%20Universities%20Have%20Been%20Sued%20By%20Thousands%20of%20Students%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20current%20and%20former%20students%20of%20University%20College%20London%20(UCL)%20are%20seeking%20compensation%2C%20claiming%20their%20tuition%20contracts%20were%20breached%20after%20teaching%20went%20online%20during%20Covid%20with%20restricted%20access%20to%20facilities.%20These%20include%20dozens%20of%20students%20from%20India%20who%20suffered%20disruption%20in%20studies%20and%20joined%20the%20mass%20lawsuit.%20The%20group%20has%20urged%20the%20London%20High%20Court%20to%20give%20the%20legal%20complaint%20its%20go%20ahead.%20According%20to%20news%20agency%20Reuters%2C%20these%20students%20have%20paid%20at%20least%209%2C250%20pounds%20(%2411%2C482)%20a%20year%20for%20studying%20at%20UCL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20successful%2C%20the%20students%20stand%20to%20win%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20pounds%20in%20compensation%20saying%20they%20were%20offered%20online%20course%20instead%20of%20what%20was%20promised%20-%20in-person%20teaching.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawyers%20running%20the%20case%20against%20UCL%20say%20around%20100%2C000%20students%20from%2018%20universities%20including%20UCL%20have%20signed%20up%20to%20bring%20legal%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20problems%20Indian%20students%20faced%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legal%20action%20has%20been%20mounted%20by%20those%20who%20studied%20in%20the%20UK%20between%202017%20and%202022.%20Among%20them%20is%20Arunima%20Ghosh%2C%20an%20MSc%20in%20applied%20bioscience%20student.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Ghosh%20said%20she%20paid%20full%20fees%20for%20the%20in-person%20experience%20at%20the%20university%20by%20offering%20her%20home%20as%20collateral%20against%20a%20loan.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20she%20was%20researching%20the%20effects%20of%20chemotherapy%20on%20cancerous%20cells%20but%20the%20university%20closed%20the%20labs%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20So%20she%20doesn't%20have%20anything%20to%20show%20as%20experiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20nothing.%20I%20paid%20all%20this%20money%20and%20received%20nothing%20that%20was%20promised%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Findian-students-mount-legal-action-against-british-universities-over-covid-disruptions%2Farticleshowprint%2F100975082.cms%5C%22%3Etold%20the%20outlet%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUniversities%20across%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20moved%20to%20online%20learning%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20with%20students%20also%20being%20denied%20access%20to%20teaching%20facilities%20such%20as%20libraries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20come%20out%20with%20a%20very%20lacklustre%20degree.%20It's%20not%20worth%20what%20I%20paid%20for.%20It%20is%20not%20of%20the%20same%20value.%20I%20don't%20have%20the%20skills%20that%20were%20promised.%20So%2C%20no%2C%20it%20was%20not%20worth%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20students%20Tia%20O'Donnell%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EChannel%205%20News%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20UCL%20has%20to%20say%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUCL%20says%20it%20did%20not%20breach%20its%20contract%20with%20students.%20The%20university%20argues%20it%20was%20permitted%20to%20change%20or%20cancel%20any%20part%20of%20its%20courses%20due%20to%20circumstances%20beyond%20its%20control%2C%20such%20as%20the%20pandemic%20and%20consequent%20lockdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20the%20Indian%20student%20faced%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaw%20firm%20Harcus%20Parker%2C%20which%20has%20taken%20up%20the%20case%20of%20the%20Indian%20students%2C%20said%20300%20have%20returned%20to%20their%20home%20country%20but%20several%20thousand%20more%20Indians%20in%20other%20countries%20are%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20Indian%20students%20spent%20an%20awful%20lot%20of%20money%20and%20got%20very%20little%20back%20for%20it%20and%20feel%20very%20disgruntled.%20In%202020%20to%202021%20teaching%20was%20shunted%20online%20in%20a%20haphazard%20manner%20and%20physical%20facilities%20were%20largely%20removed%2C%20yet%20they%20were%20paying%20these%20huge%20international%20fees%20to%20be%20given%20a%20correspondence%20course%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20firm's%20Ryan%20Dunleavy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20hearing%20in%20the%20high%20court%20took%20place%20on%20May%2024%20against%20UCL.%20Later%2C%2017%20other%20UK%20universities%20were%20sent%20letters%20before%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2017%2C%20the%20court%20asked%20both%20the%20parties%20to%20settle%20the%20claim%20out-of-court%20without%20the%20need%20for%20a%20trial%2C%20and%20has%20put%20the%20trial%20on%20pause%20for%20eight%20months.%20The%20judge%20also%20gave%20permission%20for%20either%20side%20to%20ask%20the%20court%20to%20cut%20short%20that%20period%20to%20four%20months%20in%20certain%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20students'%20body%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstudentgroupclaim.co.uk%2Fcampaign-news%2F%23content-box-block_64185a163e2de%5C%22%3Ein%20a%20blog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20studentgroupclaim.co.uk%20said%20that%20they%20will%20try%20to%20find%20an%20out-of-court%20solution%20but%20will%20move%20ahead%20with%20the%20case%20if%20it%20is%20not%20settled%20during%20the%20given%20timeframe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20respect%20the%20right%20of%20our%20students%20to%20complain%20and%20seek%20redress%20if%20they%20feel%20that%20they%20have%20not%20received%20the%20support%20they%20expected%20from%20us.%20We%20still%20believe%20our%20complaints%20procedure%20represents%20the%20most%20efficient%2C%20cost-effective%20and%20swiftest%20way%20for%20students%20to%20resolve%20their%20complaints.%20We%20are%20pleased%20that%20the%20High%20Court%20has%20ordered%20that%20proceedings%20be%20stayed%20to%20allow%20for%20the%20parties%20to%20attempt%20to%20resolve%20the%20students'%20claims%20without%20the%20need%20for%20further%20litigation%2C%20and%20that%20the%20Court%20has%20recognised%20the%20part%20our%20complaints%20procedure%20can%20play%2C%26quot%3B%20Professor%20Kathleen%20Armour%2C%20UCL's%20Vice-Provost%20(Education%20%26amp%3B%20Student%20Experience)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ucl.ac.uk%2Fnews%2F2023%2Fjul%2Fhigh-court-orders-pause-student-group-claim%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20a%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20the%20students%20succeed%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudents%20%26quot%3Bcould%20face%20an%20uphill%20battle%20to%20win%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Ff70e8b04-58b2-420d-9395-c696cb7f637b%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%20(FT)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Legal%20experts%20say%20students%20could%20struggle%20to%20quantify%20the%20size%20of%20any%20loss.%20%26quot%3BTo%20think%20of%20it%20as%20a%20price%20in%20the%20way%20you%20would%20a%20car%20or%20a%20holiday%20is%20quite%20difficult%2C%26quot%3B%20Smita%20Jamdar%2C%20head%20of%20education%20at%20law%20firm%20Shakespeare%20Martineau%2C%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAne%20Vernon%2C%20head%20of%20education%20at%20Payne%20Hicks%20Beach%2C%20told%20the%20FT%20that%20these%20sorts%20of%20cases%20were%20not%20easy%20to%20bring.%20%26quot%3BUnderstandably%20students%20are%20aggrieved%20by%20their%20university%20years%20being%20affected%20by%20Covid%20and%20industrial%20action%2C%20but%20the%20challenge%20will%20be%20to%20prove%20liability%20for%20loss%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690869780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-09%2Fc6asiv8o_women-college-students-generic-pixabay_625x300_17_September_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fstudents-including-indians-suing-uk-universities-over-covid-disruptions-heres-why-4257844%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lawyers%20running%20the%20case%20against%20University%20College%20London%20say%20around%20100%2C000%20students%20from%2018%20universities%20including%20UCL%20have%20signed%20up%20to%20bring%20legal%20action.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fstudents-including-indians-suing-uk-universities-over-covid-disruptions-heres-why-4257844%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fstudents-including-indians-suing-uk-universities-over-covid-disruptions-heres-why-4257844%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fstudents-including-indians-suing-uk-universities-over-covid-disruptions-heres-why-4257844%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Overdose%20suspected%20as%20Angus'%20death%20cause%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690869636000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102300047%2Cimgsize-27700.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Feuphoria-actor-angus-clouds-cause-of-death-suspected-as-possible-overdose-report%2Farticleshow%2F102300632.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102300632.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAngus%20Cloud%2C%20the%20breakout%20star%20of%20HBO's%20'Euphoria'%2C%20passed%20away%20on%20Monday%2C%20with%20his