20when%20it%20reached%20Nuh%20around%201%3A30%20pm.%20According%20to%20authorities%2C%20the%20Yatra%20had%20permission%2C%20and%20around%201%2C000%20policemen%20were%20deployed%20along%20the%20Yatra%E2%80%99s%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20a%20group%20of%20young%20men%20near%20Khedla%20Mod%20in%20Nuh%20stopped%20the%20Yatra%20and%20pelted%20stones%20at%20the%20procession.%20At%20least%20four%20cars%2C%20part%20of%20the%20procession%2C%20were%20set%20on%20fire.%C2%A0Some%20police%20vehicles%20were%20also%20damaged.%C2%A0People%20in%20the%20procession%20hurled%20stones%20back%20at%20the%20youths%20who%20had%20stopped%20them%2C%20the%20PTI%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20situation%20is%20tense%20in%20Nuh.%20There%20are%20about%203%2C000-4%2C000%20persons%20being%20held%20hostage%20at%20Narhar%20temple.%20All%20these%20were%20part%20of%20the%20VHP%E2%80%99s%20procession.%20We%20are%20trying%20our%20best%20to%20first%20rescue%20these%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20IE%20quoted%20state%20home%20minister%2C%20Anil%20Vij%2C%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20district%20official%20said%201%2C000%20people%20are%20held%20hostage%20at%20the%20temple%20and%20said%20efforts%20are%20on%20to%20evacuate%20them.%20%E2%80%9CForces%20from%20Faridabad%2C%20Narnaul%2C%20and%20Rewari%20have%20been%20called%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20claims%20doing%20rounds%20that%20the%20trigger%20for%20the%20clash%20was%20an%20objectionable%20video%20posted%20on%20social%20media%20by%20a%20Bajrang%20Dal%20activist%20in%20Ballabhgarh.%20Reports%20also%20indicate%20that%20Monu%20Manesar%20%E2%80%93%20a%20cow%20vigilante%20wanted%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20two%20Muslim%20men%20in%20Rajasthan%20%E2%80%93%20was%20supposed%20to%20join%20the%20procession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENuh%20MLA%20Aftab%20Ahmed%20from%20the%20Congress%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20it%20was%20really%20unfortunate%20that%20such%20events%20have%20happened%2C%20and%20held%20the%20district%20administration%20responsible%20for%20the%20flaring%20up%20of%20clashes.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20administration%20has%20failed%20in%20its%20duty%20to%20prevent%20these%20clashes%20despite%20the%20circulation%20of%20provocative%20and%20hateful%20videos%20since%20the%20last%202-3%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20could%20see%20two%20such%20videos%20where%20Hindutva%20activists%20provoked%20people%20of%20Nuh%20to%20%E2%80%9Cwelcome%E2%80%9D%20the%20rallyists%20as%20their%20Yatra%20will%20%E2%80%9Cmake%20it%20a%20point%E2%80%9D%20to%20pass%20through%20Muslim-majority%20Nuh.%20In%20the%20same%20video%2C%20the%20leader%20used%20several%20humiliating%20references%20against%20the%20people%20of%20Nuh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhmed%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSuch%20anti-social%20elements%20have%20been%20patronised%20under%20this%20government%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20They%20move%20around%20without%20any%20fear%20of%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindutva%20activists%20on%20the%20ground%20claimed%20that%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9Caround%202%2C500-3%2C000%20Hindus%E2%80%9D%20who%20had%20come%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20rally%20have%20been%20held%20%E2%80%9Chostage%E2%80%9D%20in%20a%20local%20temple%2C%20and%20need%20%E2%80%9Cevacuation%20by%20central%20forces%E2%80%9D.%20Most%20saffron%20leaders%20have%20already%20begun%20demanding%20that%20the%20Centre%20deploy%20central%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Ahmed%20refuted%20such%20a%20claim.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20such%20things%20happen%2C%20people%20take%20shelter.%20Now%20things%20have%20stopped%20flaring%20up.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20how%20the%20clashes%20broke%20out%2C%20he%20said%20that%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20the%20exact%20turn%20of%20events%20but%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20area%20is%20known%20historically%20for%20its%20cultural%20brotherhood.%20Now%2C%20it%20is%20time%20for%20us%20to%20appeal%20to%20everyone%20to%20maintain%20peace%20and%20not%20be%20part%20of%20any%20rumour%20that%20is%20being%20deliberately%20circulated%20to%20foment%20more%20clashes%20between%20the%20communities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20social%20organisation%20called%20Mewat%20Vikas%20Sabha%20informed%20the%20press%20that%20the%20Shobha%20Yatra%20was%20preceded%20by%20circulation%20of%20several%20hateful%20videos%20against%20Muslims%20in%20Mewat.%20It%20alleged%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CShobha%20Yatra%E2%80%9D%20organised%20by%20Hindutva%20groups%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccalculated%E2%80%9D%20attempt%20by%20engineer%20communal%20violence%20in%20the%20Muslim-majority%20Nuh.%20%E2%80%9CVery%20provocative%20videos%20were%20circulated%20in%20the%20last%20two%20days.%20Despite%20that%2C%20the%20administration%20allowed%20the%20Yatra%20to%20enter%20Mewat.%20And%20when%20violence%20began%2C%20the%20administration%20simply%20collapsed%2C%20police%20disappeared%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20district%20magistrate%20Nishant%20Kumar%20Yadav%20imposed%20Section%20144%2C%20prohibiting%20assembly%20of%20more%20than%20five%20persons%20in%20light%20of%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EDeputy%20Commissioner%20Shri%20Nishant%20Kumar%20Yadav%2C%20imposes%20Section%20144%20of%20Cr.PC%20in%20Gurugram%20district%2C%20effective%20immediately.%20Unlawful%20activities%2C%20road%20blockades%2C%20and%20assembly%20of%205%2B%20persons%20with%20weapons%20prohibited%20to%20maintain%20peace%20%26amp%3B%20tranquility.%20Order%20in%20force%20till%20further%20notice.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FcLFehz80kh%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FcLFehz80kh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20DC%20Gurugram%20(%40DC_Gurugram)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDC_Gurugram%2Fstatus%2F1686048056288985101%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2031%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3