%20and%20Aesthetics%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%2C%20passed%20away%20on%20July%2030%20after%20a%20brave%20battle%20with%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Kavita%20Singh%20(1964-2023)%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20remarkable%20and%20influential%20art%20historians%20of%20our%20times.%20Kavita%20was%20associated%20with%20the%20School%20of%20Arts%20and%20Aesthetics%20(SAA)%20at%20JNU%2C%20where%20she%20taught%20since%20it%20was%20founded%20in%202001%20up%20until%20a%20few%20months%20back.%20At%20SAA%2C%20she%20taught%20courses%20on%20the%20history%20of%20Indian%20painting%20and%20the%20history%20and%20politics%20of%20museums%20in%20South%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Singh%20obtained%20a%20BA%20in%20English%20Literature%20from%20Lady%20Shri%20Ram%20College%2C%20University%20of%20Delhi%2C%20in%201985%20and%20an%20MFA%20in%20Art%20History%20from%20the%20Faculty%20of%20Fine%20Arts%2C%20Maharaja%20Sayajirao%20University%2C%20Vadodara%20in%201987.%20She%20completed%20her%20Ph.D.%20in%20art%20history%20at%20Panjab%20University%2C%20Chandigarh%2C%20in%201996.%20She%20later%20joined%20as%20a%20visiting%20Lecturer%20at%20the%20College%20of%20Art%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20from%201989%20to%201991%20and%20taught%20at%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Fashion%20Technology%20from%201991%20to%201997.%20She%20was%20part%20of%20the%20Marg%20Publications%20from%202000%20to%202001%20as%20a%20research%20editor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202001%2C%20she%20joined%20the%20SAA%20as%20an%20assistant%20professor%20and%20later%20got%20appointed%20as%20its%20dean%20in%202017%2C%20a%20position%20in%20which%20she%20served%20for%20two%20years.%20In%202018%2C%20Kavita%20was%20awarded%20the%20Infosys%20Prize%20in%20Humanities%20for%20her%20extraordinary%20study%20of%20Mughal%2C%20Rajput%2C%20and%20Deccan%20Art%20as%20well%20as%20her%20insightful%20writings%20on%20the%20functions%20and%20roles%20of%20museums.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20introduced%20to%20Kavita%E2%80%99s%20work%20on%20museums%20in%20India%20when%20I%20opted%20for%20the%20optional%20paper%20on%20%E2%80%98Archives%20and%20Museum%E2%80%99%20during%20my%20undergraduate%20studies%20at%20Delhi%20University.%20Her%20paper%20%3Cem%3EA%20Public%20Failure%3F%20Museums%20and%20Audiences%20in%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20probably%20the%20first%20academic%20paper%20that%20I%20read%2C%20and%20in%20retrospect%2C%20it%20was%20at%20this%20moment%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20explore%20the%20domain%20of%20history%20further%20as%20a%20historian%20in%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKavita%20had%20an%20exceptional%20command%20of%20scholarship%20and%20provided%20deep%20and%20original%20insights%20into%20paintings%20and%20the%20issues%20with%20the%20institution%20of%20museums.%20Her%20writings%20made%20art%20history%20accessible%20to%20a%20majority%20of%20students%20and%20enthusiasts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20scholar%20who%20spoke%20truth%20to%20power%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20started%20%E2%80%98Karwaan%3A%20The%20Heritage%20Exploration%20Initiative%E2%80%99%20in%20September%202019%2C%20the%20first%20person%20that%20came%20to%20my%20mind%20to%20be%20invited%20for%20a%20session%20was%20Kavita%20Singh.%20I%20wanted%20her%20to%20speak%20on%20(strangely%20enough)%20Nandlal%20Bose%20and%20the%20paintings%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution.%20That%20wish%20of%20hosting%20Kavita%20on%20Karwaan%20came%20true%20on%20April%2029%2C%202020%2C%20when%20she%20delivered%20one%20of%20our%20first%20Karwaan%20online%20lectures%20on%20%E2%80%98Understanding%20Mughal%20Potraits%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20day%20I%20can%20never%20forget.%20After%20the%20lecture%2C%20she%20suggested%20scholars%20who%20can%20be%20hosted%20on%20our%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F31193053%2FIMG_1992.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F31193053%2FIMG_1992.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F31193053%2FIMG_1992-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F31193053%2FIMG_1992-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-666023%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDr.%20Kavita%20Singh%20(centre).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20amongst%20the%20rare%20kind%20of%20scholars%20%E2%80%93%20scholars%20who%20had%20the%20spine%20to%20speak%20out%20whenever%20necessary%20and%20who%20stood%20by%20their%20beliefs.%20She%20spoke%20out%20when%20things%20started%20deteriorating%20at%20JNU.%20While%20accepting%20the%20Infosys%20Prize%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20never%20had%20much%20money%20or%20facilities%2C%20but%20we%20had%20excellent%20colleagues%20and%20academic%20freedom.%20Today%2C%20things%20are%20bad%3B%20things%20are%20comically%20bad%20in%20my%20institutional%20home.%20How%20bad%20you%20may%20ask%3F%20After%20I%20came%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20I%20checked%20my%20e-mail%20and%20found%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dnu2iSnXFK3Y%5C%22%3Eleave%20application%20I%20had%20put%20in%20to%20come%20here%20and%20receive%20the%20award%20had%20been%20rejected%20by%20my%20vice-chancellor%3C%2Fa%3E.%20So%20please%20be%20warned%20that%20my%20presence%20on%20this%20stage%20today%20is%20illegitimate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20stood%20for%20what%20was%20right%20and%20just%2C%20never%20afraid%20of%20speaking%20out%20about%20injustices.%20Kavita%20also%20was%20a%20champion%20of%20academic%20freedom%20and%20had%20hosted%20historian%20Audrey%20Truschke%20for%20a%20lecture%20in%20JNU%20despite%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20being%20an%20internationally%20respected%20scholar%20on%20miniature%20paintings%20and%20museum%20studies%2C%20Kavita%20was%20an%20exceptional%20human%20being.%20One%20of%20the%20kindest%2C%20sweetest%2C%20and%20most%20brilliant%20persons%20I%20have%20known.%20She%20was%20always%20up%20for%20her%20students%20and%20friends.%20She%20was%20always%20very%20encouraging%20and%20supportive%20to%20all.%20I%20was%20never%20taught%20by%20Dr.%20Kavita%20Singh%20formally%20in%20a%20classroom%2C%20but%20all%20my%20interactions%20and%20conversations%20with%20her%20were%20deeply%20enriching%20and%20enlightening.%20I%20was%20always%20in%20awe%20of%20her%20brilliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fkavita-singhs-inspiring-research-and-memories-of-her-unwavering-kindness-will-live-on%5C%22%3EKavita%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20Inspiring%20Research%20%E2%80%93%20and%20Memories%20of%20Her%20Unwavering%20Kindness%20%E2%80%93%20Will%20Live%20On%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20anyone%20who%20is%20new%20to%20the%20world%20of%20art%20or%20art%20history%2C%20any%20writing%20or%20article%20by%20Kavita%20Singh%20or%20any%20lecture%20of%20hers%20on%20YouTube%20can%20make%20you%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20the%20discipline.%20I%20was%20always%20very%20envious%20of%20my%20friends%20who%20were%20students%20of%20Kavita%20at%20JNU%20but%20made%20up%20for%20it%20by%20attending%20her%20lectures%20online%20on%20various%20occasions%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20Her%20scholarship%20always%20provided%20a%20deep%20insight%20into%20one%20or%20the%20other%20underappreciated%20aspects%20of%20a%20painting%20that%20she%20was%20talking%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202023%2C%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20her%20to%20deliver%20the%20inaugural%20Karwaan%20Keynote%20in%20Delhi%20to%20which%20she%20responded%20promptly.%20Just%20a%20fortnight%20ago%2C%20on%20July%2015%2C%20Kavita%20delivered%20the%20inaugural%20Karwaan%20Keynote.%20The%20hall%20was%20jampacked.%20Everyone%20wanted%20to%20listen%20to%20Dr.%20Kavita%20Singh%20talk%20about%20Kashi%20Ramayana%2C%20a%20lesser-known%20but%20magnificent%20manuscript-illustration%20project%20of%20the%2018th-19th%20century%20from%20Varanasi.%20She%20was%20not%20well%20and%20informed%20us%20to%20arrange%20a%20table%20and%20a%20chair%20on%20stage%20but%20notwithstanding%20anything%20she%20delivered%20her%20lecture%20at%20her%20best%20for%20almost%20an%20hour%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20Q%26amp%3BA%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FPtqxg3wUu2c%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20one%20of%20the%20bravest%20and%20the%20most%20resilient%20of%20us%20all.%20Her%20presentation%20was%20received%20by%20a%20massive%20round%20of%20applause%20and%20a%20standing%20ovation%20from%20everyone%20in%20the%20audience.%20She%20mentioned%20to%20me%20how%20happy%20she%20was%20around%20friends%20and%20students%20and%20she%20was%20still%20thinking%20of%20finishing%20a%20writing%20project%20for%20the%20Museum%20of%20Photography%20in%20Bangalore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20student%20of%20SAA%20remarked%20that%20it%20was%20as%20if%20she%20was%20taking%20a%20class%20at%20the%20SAA.%20That%20day%20was%20truly%20memorable%2C%20I%20got%20to%20spend%20a%20few%20unforgettable%20moments%20with%20a%20true%20scholar%2C%20who%20was%20so%20passionately%20dedicated%20to%20her%20craft.%20Kavita%20was%20always%20so%20appreciative%20and%20encouraging.%20When%20she%20entered%20the%20auditorium%20that%20day%2C%20she%20asked%20me%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20sure%20you%20have%20got%2048%20hours%20in%20a%20day%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20of%20her%20passing%20came%20as%20a%20sudden%20shock.%20The%20loss%20of%20a%20friend%2C%20erudite%20scholar%2C%20fighter%2C%20and%20activist%2C%20Dr.%20Kavita%20Singh%2C%20is%20a%20personal%20loss%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20us.%20I%20will%20always%20remember%20her%20generosity%2C%20kindness%2C%20and%20that%20contagious%20smile%20of%20Kavita.%20Her%20grace%2C%20knowledge%2C%20humility%2C%20and%20brilliance%20were%20unmatched.%20We%20have%20lost%20one%20of%20the%20best%20and%20true%20scholars.%20No%20words%20can%20justify%20what%20Kavita%20meant%20to%20us%20as%20a%20mentor%2C%20friend%2C%20and%20scholar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdieu%20Kavita%2C%20you%20will%20be%20dearly%20missed.%20My%20heart%20breaks%20as%20I%20write%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEshan%20Sharma%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20Karwaan%3A%20The%20Heritage%20Exploration%20Initiative.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690857049000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F31192120%2FUntitled-design-2023-07-31T192045.561.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fkavita-singh-1964-2023-a-remarkable-historian-whose-writings-made-art-history-accessible%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22To%20anyone%20who%20is%20new%20to%20the%20world%20of%20art%20or%20art%20history%2C%20any%20writing%20or%20article%20by%20Kavita%20Singh%20or%20any%20lecture%20of%20hers%20on%20YouTube%20can%20make%20you%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20the%20discipline.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fkavita-singh-1964-2023-a-remarkable-historian-whose-writings-made-art-history-accessible%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%229%20Times%20Mrunal%20proved%20that%20black%20is%20HOT!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690857000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102282676%2Cimgsize-45440.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhi