%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffemale-ukrainian-soldiers-suffer-lack-of-womens-resources-report-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EInsider%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224096%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Several%20female%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20pose%20for%20a%20photo%20while%20holding%20their%20Zemliachky%20humanitarian%20boxes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c85088048ff200190e86dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222731%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZemliachky%20has%20supported%20thousands%20of%20women%20since%20the%20war%20began.%20%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Zemliachky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWartime%20pregnancies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20one%20female%20soldier%20in%20particular%20%E2%80%94%20a%20sniper%20to%20whom%20Zemliachky%20had%20previously%20sent%20aid%20%E2%80%94%20who%20reached%20back%20out%20to%20the%20organization%20and%20inquired%20about%20a%20uniform%20that%20could%20accommodate%20her%20pregnancy%2C%20the%20founders%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20soldier%20finds%20out%20she's%20pregnant%2C%20she's%20immediately%20removed%20from%20any%20combat%20roles%2C%20though%20Kolesnyk%20said%20the%20sniper%20first%20hid%20her%20pregnancy%20for%20nearly%20three%20months%20as%20she%20sought%20to%20continue%20her%20frontline%20duties.%20The%20danger%20and%20discomfort%20of%20hours%20on%20her%20stomach%20near%20the%20frontlines%2C%20however%2C%20eventually%20convinced%20her%20to%20pull%20back%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Zemliachky%20posted%20about%20the%20military%20uniform%20pants%20they%20sent%20her%20that%20can%20adjust%20to%20fit%20a%20growing%20belly%2C%20Kolesnyk%20said%20more%20requests%20from%20pregnant%20soldiers%20started%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPregnant%20women%20enlisted%20in%20Ukraine's%20army%20continue%20to%20serve%20up%20to%20seven%20months%20into%20their%20pregnancy%2C%20the%20couple%20said%2C%20necessitating%20uniforms%20that%20fit%20like%20%26quot%3Ba%20second%20skin.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImagine%20if%20we%20take%20all%20the%20men%20in%20all%20the%20armies%20in%20the%20world%20and%20give%20them%20female%20uniforms%2C%26quot%3B%20Kolesnyk%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20should%20females%20wear%20their%20uniforms%3F%20They%20do%20the%20same%20job%2C%20hold%20the%20same%20positions%20in%20the%20army.%20They%20should%20work%20in%20comfort.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EArmor%2C%20ammunition%2C%20and%20weddings%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKolesnyk%20and%20Drahaniuk%20said%20they%20were%20inspired%20to%20launch%20Zemliachky%20after%20Kolesnyk's%20sister%2C%20Anastasia%2C%20enlisted%20last%20year%20and%20soon%20sent%20the%20couple%20a%20laundry%20list%20of%20basic%20items%20she%20was%20lacking.%20The%20duo%20sent%20Anastasia%20Zemliachky's%20first%20ever%20%26quot%3Bhumanitarian%20box%26quot%3B%20featuring%20a%20collection%20of%2030%20different%20female%20hygiene%20products%20and%20medicines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20couple%20began%20posting%20about%20the%20nonprofit's%20work%20on%20social%20media%2C%20their%20following%20grew%2C%20and%20word-of-mouth%20chatter%20among%20female%20soldiers%20soon%20brought%20in%20more%20and%20more%20requests%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20more%20people%20get%20to%20know%20us%2C%20the%20more%20they%20can%20tell%20their%20friends%20that%20this%20foundation%20supports%20women%2C%20and%20any%20female%20soldier%20can%20write%20to%20us%20on%20Instagram%2C%26quot%3B%20Kolesnyk%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20months%20since%20they%20started%2C%20the%20organization%20has%20supported%20thousands%20of%20women%20in%20the%20army%2C%20sending%20more%20than%20%24200%20million%20worth%20of%20armor%2C%20ammunition%2C%20helmets%2C%20clothing%2C%20shoes%2C%20first%20aid%20kits%2C%20and%20hygiene%20products%20to%20female%20soldiers%20scattered%20throughout%20Ukraine%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Zemliachky%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20outfitting%20Ukraine's%20female%20soldiers%2C%20Zemliachky%20also%20helps%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnewlywed-soldiers-ukraine-russia-invasion-frontlines-hope-grow-old-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eorganize%20weddings%20and%20honeymoons%20for%20Ukrainian%20service%20members%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20offers%20women%20in%20the%20army%20access%20to%2010%20free%20therapy%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20exuberant%20photos%20of%20women%20posing%20in%20their%20new%20uniforms%20and%20the%20videos%20of%20joy-filled%20weddings%20make%20the%20work%20worthwhile%2C%20Kolesnyk%20and%20Drahaniuk%20said.%20But%20the%20heartwarming%20moments%20are%20oft-tempered%20by%20the%20realities%20of%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20hundreds%20of%20sad%20stories%20behind%20every%20one%20inspiring%20story%2C%26quot%3B%20Kolesnyk%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20situations%20when%20we%20get%20requests%20for%20a%20uniform%20for%20a%20pregnant%20woman%2C%20but%20when%20we%20make%20it%2C%20we%20do%20not%20send%20it%20because%20we%20get%20a%20message%20that%20this%20woman%20lost%20her%20child.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20also%20described%20instances%20of%20sending%20out%20humanitarian%20boxes%20to%20female%20soldiers%20only%20for%20the%20items%20to%20be%20returned%20%E2%80%94%20the%20women%20in%20need%20no%20longer%20alive%20to%20use%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20inspiring%20stories%2C%20but%20we%20can't%20say%20they're%20always%20inspiring%20because%20we%20are%20talking%20about%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20Kolesnyk%20said.%20%26quot%3BAll%20these%20stories%20will%20be%20called%20inspiring%20when%20we%20achieve%20victory.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpregnant-ukrainian-soldie