0said%20that%20ex%20gratia%20compensation%20will%20be%20given%20to%20the%20families%20of%20those%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EP.C.%20Sinha%2C%20Inspector%20General%20cum%20Principal%20Chief%20Security%20Commissioner%2C%20Western%20Railway%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CConstable%20Chetan%20Singh%20is%20a%20short-tempered%20person%20and%20suffering%20from%20mental%20health%20issues.%20He%20first%20shot%20his%20superior%20and%20then%20shot%20those%20who%20came%20in%20front%20of%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690840270000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F16111107%2F5264934981_08748b0f32_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Frailway-protection-force-constable-shoots-dead-asi-three-others-in-train%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20purported%20video%20of%20RPF%20constable%20Chetan%20Kumar%20shows%20him%20standing%20beside%20a%20bloodied%20body%20telling%20other%20passengers%20that%20if%20they%20want%20to%20vote%20and%20live%20in%20India%2C%20'Modi%20and%20Yogi%2C%20these%20are%20the%20two%2C%20and%20your%20Thackeray'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Frailway-protection-force-constable-shoots-dead-asi-three-others-in-train%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Angus%20Cloud%2C%20%E2%80%98Euphoria%E2%80%99%20Star%2C%20Dead%20at%2025%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690840006000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAngus-Cloud-Dead.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235684089%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Angus%20Cloud%2C%20the%20actor%20best%20known%20for%20playing%20the%20drug%20dealer%20Fezco%20%E2%80%9CFez%E2%80%9D%20O%E2%80%99Neill%20on%20HBO%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CEuphoria%2C%E2%80%9D%20has%20died%20at%2025%20years%20old.%20TMZ%20first%20reported