%20New%20Hampshire%20%E2%80%94%20the%20critical%20early-voting%20battleground%20which%20could%20provide%20momentum%20for%20the%20eventual%20GOP%20nominee%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20all%20getting%20invaluable%20face%20time%20with%20the%20very%20same%20voters%20who'll%20help%20set%20the%20direction%20for%20the%20party%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20candidates%20not%20named%20Donald%20Trump%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20ground%20to%20make%20up%2C%20as%20the%20former%20president%20retains%20polling%20advantages%20not%20only%20nationally%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprojects.fivethirtyeight.com%2Fpolls%2Fnew-hampshire%2F%5C%22%3Ein%20the%20Granite%20State%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Gov.%20Ron%20DeSantis%20of%20Florida%20was%20widely%20expected%20to%20put%20a%20dent%20in%20Trump's%20lead%20when%20he%20launched%20his%20campaign%20in%20May%2C%20the%20former%20president's%20political%20position%20has%20so%20far%20remained%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeSantis%20has%20heavily%20touted%20after%20enacting%20plenty%20of%20conservative%20policies%20in%20Florida%20as%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20his%20candidacy%2C%20but%20New%20Hampshire%20Gov.%20Chris%20Sununu%20on%20Monday%20said%20that%20policy%20alone%20wouldn't%20be%20enough%20to%20capture%20the%20GOP%20nomination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20speaking%20to%20Hugh%20Hewitt%20on%20the%20conservative%20author's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBnfvJtidDio%5C%22%3Epodcast%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sununu%20said%20that%20DeSantis%20would%20have%20to%20get%20personal%20with%20voters%20and%20show%20them%20his%20authenticity%20if%20he%20wanted%20to%20make%20real%20inroads%20with%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20talking%20to%20DeSantis%20about%20this%20and%20all%20that.%20I%20said%2C%20don't%20worry%20about%20the%20policy%20stuff.%20We've%20got%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Sununu%20told%20Hewitt.%20%26quot%3BYou've%20got%20to%20be%20about%20character%2C%20about%20looking%20people%20in%20the%20eye%2C%20and%20you've%20got%20to%20show%20that%20you're%20not%20just%20viable%20to%20stand%20on%20the%20stage.%20You're%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20one%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20stage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20the%20leader%2C%20you%20are%20the%20winner%2C%20you're%20the%20person%20that%20is%20going%20to%20inspire%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20party%20to%20get%20bigger%20and%20more%20excited%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20governor%20continued.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20it's%20really%20about%2C%20kind%20of%2C%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20that%20charisma%20and%20leadership%20that%20they've%20got%20to%20show%20to%20folks%20one-on-one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20University%20of%20New%20Hampshire%20%3Ca%20data-v9y%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-ylk%3D%5C%22slk%3Asurvey%3Belm%3Acontext_link%3Bitc%3A0%5C%22%20data-rapid_p%3D%5C%227%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscholars.unh.edu%2Fsurvey_center_polls%2F749%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Trump%20led%20with%2037%25%20support%2C%20with%20DeSantis%20in%20second%20place%20with%2023%25%2C%20while%20Sen.%20Tim%20Scott%20of%20South%20Carolina%20came%20in%20third%20with%208%25%2C%20followed%20by%20Gov.%20Doug%20Burgum%20of%20North%20Dakota%20and%20former%20Gov.%20Chris%20Christie%20of%20New%20Jersey%20each%20earning%206%25%20support.%20Entrepreneur%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20and%20former%20Gov.%20Nikki%20Haley%20of%20South%20Carolina%20each%20took%20in%205%25%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESununu%20recently%20argued%20that%20Trump%20polling%20below%2050%25%20in%20New%20Hampshire%20gave%20other%20candidates%20a%20huge%20opportunity%20to%20make%20the%20case%20for%20their%20respective%20candidacies.%20But%20he%20also%20stated%20that%20the%20other%20candidates%20had%20to%20be%20willing%20to%20go%20after%20the%20former%20president's%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEither%20you're%20willing%20to%20swing%2C%20you're%20willing%20to%20give%20the%20punch%20and%20take%20the%20punch%20and%20show%20leadership%2C%20or%20you're%20kowtowing%2C%26quot%3B%20Sununu%20said%20during%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsununu-trump-2024-gop-presidential-candidates-swing-christie-hutchinson-2023-7%5C%22%3Ean%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Fox%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsununu-desantis-eye-contact-charisma-leadership-2024-gop-primary-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690839500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63e55e7b27e5db0018eefbe5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsununu-desantis-eye-contact-charisma-leadership-2024-gop-primary-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chris%20Sununu%20said%20that%20Ron%20DeSantis%20would%20have%20to%20get%20personal%20with%20voters%20and%20show%20them%20his%20character%20if%20he%20wanted%20to%20make%20real%20inroads%20with%20voters.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(John%20L.%20Dorman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsununu-desantis-eye-contact-charisma-leadership-2024-gop-primary-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Joaquin%20Phoenix%20Slapped%20Vanessa%20Kirby%20in%20%E2%80%98Napoleon%E2%80%99%20After%20They%20Agreed%20to%20%E2%80%98Shock%20Each%20Other%E2%80%99%3B%20She%20Told%20Him%3A%20%E2%80%98You%20Can%20Slap%20Me%2C%20Grab%20Me%2C%20Pull%20Me%2C%20Kiss%20Me%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690839183000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FScreen-Shot-2023-07-31-at-3.54.12-PM-1.png%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235683742%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Joaquin%20Phoenix%20and%20Vanessa%20Kirby%20told%20Empire%20magazine%