e%20app.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20cut%20makes%20Instacart%20workers%20more%20reliant%20on%20customers'%20tips%20and%20claiming%20the%20best-paying%20orders.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDrivers%20at%20many%20gig%20delivery%20services%20say%20their%20earnings%20have%20fallen%20from%20highs%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20who%20deliver%20your%20groceries%20through%20Instacart%20just%20took%20a%20big%20pay%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrivers%20for%20the%20delivery%20service%20are%20now%20paid%20a%20minimum%20of%20%244%20per%20order%2C%20down%20from%20%247%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company%20and%20interviews%20and%20screenshots%20from%20three%20drivers.%20The%20cut%20affects%20base%20pay%2C%20or%20an%20amount%20that%20Instacart%20workers%20are%20guaranteed%20to%20get%20if%20they%20accept%20an%20order.%20They%20can%20earn%20more%20from%20customer%20tips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstacart%20announced%20the%20lower%20base%20pay%20in%20a%20July%2020%20blog%20post%20entitled%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dc28c1071ca90ac112572f09970f215568b5992df2e52fd061d622887c0c24b86%26postID%3D64c7e726c32d1aa092d05b04%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.instacart.com%252Fcompany%252Fshopper-community%252Fcreating-new-ways-to-earn%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bcreating%20new%20ways%20to%20earn.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20In%20the%20post%2C%20Instacart%20said%20orders%20that%20involve%20picking%20and%20delivering%20many%20items%20%26quot%3Bmay%20pay%20%2410%20or%20more%26quot%3B%20in%20base%20pay.%20Drivers%20that%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20said%20that%20they%20noticed%20the%20cut%20in%20their%20pay%20over%20the%20last%20week%20or%20so.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20driver%20who%20delivers%20for%20Instacart%20in%20Tennessee%20told%20Insider%20that%20they%20noticed%20the%20lower%20base%20pay%20on%20orders%20as%20early%20as%20last%20week.%20%26quot%3BI've%20seen%20it%20anywhere%20from%20%244.86%20to%20%247.02%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20driver%20said%20of%20base%20pay%20on%20orders.%20The%20driver%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20identified%2C%20citing%20concerns%20over%20potential%20retaliation%20from%20Instacart.%20Insider%20has%20verified%20their%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstacart's%20blog%20post%20says%20that%20orders%20with%20at%20least%20%244%20in%20base%20pay%20might%20involve%20%26quot%3Bdelivering%20a%20bag%20of%20chips%20or%20a%20pint%20of%20ice%20cream.%26quot%3B%20But%20screenshots%20sent%20to%20Insider%20by%20Instacart%20shoppers%20from%20the%20last%20few%20days%20show%20more%20complex%20orders.%20One%20order%20sent%20by%20a%20shopper%20in%20Indiana%20required%20driving%20just%20over%20a%20mile%20from%20the%20store%20%E2%80%94%20but%20only%20after%20picking%20up%2045%20items%20in%20at%20a%20grocery%20store%20for%20pay%20of%20just%20under%20%247.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDaniel%20Danker%2C%20chief%20product%20officer%20at%20Instacart%2C%20said%20that%20the%20company%20adjusted%20base%20pay%20to%20account%20for%20orders%20of%20different%20sizes%20and%20complexity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShoppers%20also%20have%20full%20control%20over%20which%20batches%20they%20take%2C%20and%20we%20never%20penalize%20them%20for%20not%20accepting%20an%20order%20when%20it%20comes%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20Danker%20said.%20%26quot%3BWith%20these%20updates%2C%20we%20expect%20average%20pay%20to%20stay%20the%20same%20for%20shoppers%20across%20the%20platform.%20We%20know%20that%20not%20all%20orders%20are%20created%20equal%2C%20and%20we%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20shopper%20earnings%20reflect%20the%20effort%20needed%20to%20fulfill%20each%20batch.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstacart%20confirmed%20that%20the%20change%20took%20effect%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tennessee%20driver%2C%20who%20has%20been%20working%20for%20Instacart%20for%20six%20years%2C%20said%20that%20they%20made%20%24200%20delivering%20for%20the%20service%20last%20week%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Bthe%20worst%20I've%20had%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20driver.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20first%20started%20Instacart%2C%20it%20was%20easy%20to%20make%20%241%2C000%20a%20week%26quot%3B%20by%20working%20up%20to%2030%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlexia%20Hudson%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20South%20Carolina%20and%20delivers%20for%20Instacart%20around%20the%20Charlotte%20metro%20area%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20she's%20also%20noticed%20the%20lower%20base%20pay%20in%20recent%20orders.%20Over%20the%20last%20week%2C%20the%20only%20shopping%20trips%20she's%20made%20through%20Instacart%20that%20have%20paid%20more%20than%20%247%20have%20either%20been%20orders%20with%20dozens%20of%20items%20or%20what%20Instacart%20calls%20%26quot%3Bbatches%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20multiple%20orders%20that%20the%20service%20groups%20together%20for%20a%20shopper%20to%20fill%20on%20the%20same%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELower%20batch%20pay%20is%20just%20the%20latest%20hit%20to%20Hudson's%20income%20through%20Instacart.%20She%20told%20Insider%20that%20her%20earnings%20started%20to%20dip%20this%20spring%3A%20She%20noticed%20fewer%20orders%20available%20and%20more%20people%20trying%20to%20claim%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20the%20pay%20has%20gone%20down%2C%20it's%20not%20worth%20it%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she's%20looking%20for%20a%20full-time%20job%20to%20replace%20her%20delivery%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELower%20base%20pay%20means%20more%20reliance%20on%20tips%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Hudson%20and%20the%20driver%20in%20Tennessee%20said%20that%20the%20base%20pay%20cut%20makes%20customers'%20tips%20a%20more%20important%20source%20of%20income.%20%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20serve%20tables%20back%20in%20the%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Tennessee%20driver%20said%2C%20comparing%20working%20for%20Instacart%20to%20a%20job%20at%20a%20restaurant%20where%20employees%20are%20only%20paid%20a%20few%20dollars%20an%20hour%20and%20rely%20on%20gratuities%20for%20most%20of%20their%20income.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20that.%20You'd%20rely%20heavily%20on%20those%20tips.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESergio%20Avedian%2C%20a%20spokesman%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftherideshareguy.com%2F%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftherideshareguy.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3EThe%20Rideshare%20Guy%3C%2Fa%3E%20blog%20and%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20said%20Instacart's%20base%20pay%20slashing%20is%20part%20of%20a%20growing%20trend%20among%20many%20delivery%20and%20rideshare%20apps%20in%20their%20%26quot%3Brush%26quot%3B%20to%20reach%20profitability.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20happening%20everywhere.%20They're%20all%20doing%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Avedian%2C%20an%20Uber%20Eats%20and%20DoorDash%20driver.%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20finally%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20arbitrage%20the%20power%20of%20the%20app.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trend%20for%20apps%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20charging%20as%20much%20as%20they%20can%20to%20the%20passenger%20and%20%26quot%3Bpaying%20as%20little%20as%20they%20can%20to%20the%20driver.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20been%20the%20case%20for%20Avedian.%20He%20makes%20food%20deliveries%20for%20DoorDash%20and%20Uber%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%20He%20said%20his%20average%20base%20pay%20is%20about%20%241%20per%20mile%20%E2%80%94%2050%25%20less%20than%20during%20the%20height%20of%20the%20pandemic%20when%20earnings%20surged%20due%20to%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELower%20earnings%20are%20hitting%20delivery%20drivers%20as%20inflation%20has%20pushed%20prices%20for%20everything%20higher%2C%20from%20gas%20to%20food.%20%26quot%3BEspecially%20when%20things%20are%20costing%20more%2C%20you%20should%20be%20giving%20increases%2C%20not%20decreases%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Instacart%20driver%20in%20Tennessee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20for%20Instacart%20and%20have%20a%20story%20idea%20to%20share%3F%20Write%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20