comparable%20to%20earlier%20instances%20of%20inter-communal%20conflict%3F%20Why%20is%20the%20BJP%20unwilling%20to%20dispense%20with%20chief%20minister%20Biren%20Singh%3F%20And%20is%20Manipur%20worse%20than%20Punjab%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9880s%2C%20Kashmir%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9890s%20and%20Gujarat%20in%20the%202000s%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoining%20me%20now%20to%20reveal%20his%20answer%20to%20those%20questions%20is%20Ramachandra%20Guha%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERam%20Guha%2C%20in%20a%20rather%20insightful%20op-ed%20for%20the%20paper%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20you%20wrote%20yesterday%2C%20you%20make%20several%20important%20points%20about%20the%20Manipur%20tragedy%2C%20which%20I%20would%20like%20to%20discuss%20with%20you%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20you%20point%20out%20how%20the%20inter-communal%20conflict%20in%20Manipur%20is%20significantly%20different%20to%20inter-communal%20conflicts%20we%E2%80%99ve%20previously%20seen%20in%20other%20states.%20The%20first%20difference%20is%20the%20proportionately%20greater%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-looted-weaponry-yet-to-return-to-police-armouries-cm-appeals-afresh-for-surrender%5C%22%3Eavailability%20of%20armed%20weapons%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20the%20combatants%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20Manipur.%20And%20you%20add%2C%20the%20widespread%20looting%20of%20police%20armouries%20recently%20witnessed%20in%20Manipur%2C%20perhaps%20has%20no%20parallel%20in%20Indian%20history.%20Does%20this%20make%20Manipur%20particularly%20worrisome%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERamachandra%20Guha%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Yes%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20violence%2C%20Karan%2C%20of%20course%2C%20there%20is%20a%20history%20of%20insurgency%20and%20discontent%20in%20the%20state.%20And%20the%20three%20major%20communities%20in%20the%20state%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Meiteis%2C%20the%20Nagas%20and%20the%20Kukis%20%E2%80%93%20have%20all%2C%20at%20different%20times%20armed%20themselves%20to%20varying%20degrees.%20So%2C%20there%20is%20a%20history%20of%20using%20sophisticated%20arms%20by%20ordinary%20citizens%2C%20not%20by%20the%20state%20or%20the%20police%20or%20the%20paramilitary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20usually%20these%20were%20radicals%20or%20terrorists%20or%20insurgents%20or%20separatists%20or%20whatever%20you%20might%20call%20them%2C%20seeking%20autonomy%20or%20independence%20from%20the%20Indian%20state%20using%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20they%E2%80%99re%20using%20them%20against%20one%20another%2C%20on%20a%20scale%20probably%20never%20previously%20witnessed%20in%20an%20inter-communal%20conflict%20within%20an%20Indian%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19203619%2FFyQ9vBxaIAAY1u3-1024x754.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22679%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19203619%2FFyQ9vBxaIAAY1u3-1024x754.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19203619%2FFyQ9vBxaIAAY1u3-300x221.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19203619%2FFyQ9vBxaIAAY1u3.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-659022%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGun%20drop%20box%20placed%20in%20Imphal%20Manipur.%20Authorities%20are%20asking%20people%20to%20voluntarily%20return%20snatched%20and%20looted%20weapons.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20you%20know%2C%20there%20have%20been%2C%20as%20I%20say%20in%20my%20article%2C%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20and%20Punjab%20and%20North%20India%2C%20Hindus%20and%20Sikhs%2C%20in%20other%20states.%20But%20there%E2%80%99s%20never%20been%20this%20kind%20of%20use%20of%20sophisticated%20arms%20to%20that%20level%2C%20both%20because%20of%20the%20history%20of%20using%20arms%20and%20also%20this%20widespread%20looting%20of%20armouries%2C%20which%20shows%20a%20complete%20breakdown%20in%20law%20and%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Which%20suggests%20to%20me%20that%20we%20have%20a%20situation%20which%20is%20verging%20upon%20civil%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERG%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20mixture%20of%20anarchy%20and%20civil%20war.%20After%2C%20you%20know%2C%20I%20wrote%20that%20piece%20Karan%2C%20there%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fwhen-a-kuki-college-student-in-police-custody-was-beaten-to-death-by-mob-in-manipur%2Farticle67112812.ece%5C%22%3Ereport%20of%20an%20incident%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20a%20young%20man%20from%20one%20community%20%E2%80%93%20I%20won%E2%80%99t%20name%20the%20communities%20%E2%80%93%20a%20young%20man%20from%20one%20community%20had%20been%20detained%20by%20the%20state%2C%20by%20the%20police%2C%20and%20the%20police%20released%20him%20to%20a%20mob%20from%20the%20other%20community%20who%20bludgeoned%20him%20to%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20does%20this%20tell%20you%20about%E2%80%A6%20So%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20civil%20war%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20anarchy.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20Manipur%20state%20administration%20having%20no%20control%20over%20its%20police%20and%20turning%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20mob%20violence%2C%20which%20is%E2%80%A6%20and%20of%20course%2C%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-video-two-kuki-women-paraded-naked-gang-raped%5C%22%3Eearlier%20case%20of%20a%20video%20that%20was%20widely%20circulated%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20of%20rape%2C%20of%20attacks%20on%20women.%20The%20police%20are%20aiding%20mobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20this%20is%20actually%20not%20just%20civil%20war%2C%20but%20anarchy%20and%20complete%20breakdown%20of%20the%20state%20administration.%20Perhaps%20willingly%20%E2%80%93%20because%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20deal%20with%20this%20later%2C%20perhaps%20because%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20his%20cabinet%2C%20you%20know%2C%20have%20taken%20sides%20in%20this%20civil%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Without%20revealing%20the%20identity%20and%20which%20community%20that%20young%20man%20belongs%20to%2C%20I%20simply%20tell%20the%20audience%20that%20story%20was%20in%20yesterday%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20newspaper%2C%20and%20it%20was%20exclusive%20for%20that%20paper%2C%20as%20far%20as%20I%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20the%20second%20major%20difference%20between%20Manipur%20and%20earlier%20inter-communal%20conflicts%20is%20what%20you%20call%20the%20extreme%20territorial%20separation%20that%20the%20conflict%20has%20produced.%20You%20point%20out%20that%20even%20Gujarat%20in%202002%20did%20not%20separate%20Muslims%20and%20Hindus%2C%20in%20cities%20like%20Ahmedabad%2C%20the%20way%20the%20Kukis%20and%20Meiteis%20have%20become%20separated%20both%20geographically%20and%20demographically%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERG%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Of%20course.%20In%20Manipur%2C%20which%20is%20broadly%20divided%20into%20the%20valley%20and%20the%20hills%E2%80%A6%20In%20the%20valley%2C%20the%20Meiteis%20were%20dominant%2C%20but%20there%20was%20still%20a%20significant%20minority%20of%20Kukis%20and%20Nagas.%20In%20the%20Kuki%20districts%20such%20as%20Churachandpur%2C%20the%20Kukis%20were%20dominant%20demographically%2C%20but%20there%20was%20a%20significant%20minority%20of%20Meiteis%20working%20as%20teachers%2C%20doctors%2C%20traders%2C%20labourers%2C%20whatever%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20that%20kind%20of%20ethnic%20cleansing%2C%20willing%20or%20unwilling%2C%20on%20both%20sides%E2%80%A6%20I%20mentioned%20the%20case%20of%20Ahmedabad%2C%20where%20there%20is%20a%20ghettoisation%20of%20Muslims.%20You%20know%2C%20particularly%20post-2002%20riots%2C%20they%20were%20often%20denied%20easy%20access%20to%20municipal%20facilities.%20Muslim%20couples%2C%20even%20upper-middle%20class%20Muslim%20couples%2C%20cannot%20get%20a%20house%20in%20a%20flat%2C%20which%20is%20dominated%20by%20Hindus%20and%20Jains.%20So%20there%20is%20a%20kind%20of%20segregation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20also%2C%20you%20know%2C%20a%20feeling%20among%20some%20radical%20Hindus%20that%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20Muslims%20must%20be%20consistently%20shown%20their%20place.%20But%20this%20kind%20of%20total%20separation%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20as%20if%20Ahmedabad%20was%20purged%20of%20Muslims%20totally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOr%2C%20say%20a%20majority-dominated%20district%20in%2C%20shall%20we%20say%2C%20in%20Kerala%2C%20%5Bcorrects%20himself%5D%20a%20minority-dominated%20district%2C%20like%20Malappuram%2C%20was%20purged%20of%20Hindus%20or%20Christians%20completely.%20If%20Kerala%20was%20divided%20into%20three%20%E2%80%93%20Kerala%20is%20comparable%20because%20Kerala%2C%20like%20Manipur%2C%20has%20three%20major%20communities%3A%20the%20Hindus%2C%20who%20are%20just%20sort%20of%20a%20numerical%20majority%2C%20and%20the%20Christians%20and%20the%20Muslims%20who%20are%20significant%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImagine%20Kerala%20being%20separated%20in%20three%20zones%3A%20in%20one%20zone%2C%20there%20are%20only%20Malayali%20Hindus%2C%20in%20one%20zone%2C%20there%20are%20only%20Malayali%20Christians%2C%20in%20one%20zone%2C%20there%20are%20only%20Malayali%20Muslims.%20I%20mean%2C%20that%20is%20where%20we%20are%20headed%20towards%20%5Bin%5D%20Manipur.%20I%20mean%2C%20Kerala%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20progressive%20states%20in%20India.%20We%20will%20talk%20about%20it.%20You%20just%20imagine%2C%20that%20will%20be%20the%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20mean%2C%20this%20analogy%20comes%20to%20me%20as%20I%E2%80%99m%20talking%20to%20you.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20put%20it%20in%20my%20article.%20But%20perhaps%20it%E2%80%99s%20even%20more%20compelling%2C%20because%20the%20demographic%20composition%20of%20these%20three%20communities%20in%20Kerala%2C%20with%20the%20Hindus%20being%20close%20to%20a%20majority%2C%20and%20the%20Christians%20and%20the%20Muslims%20being%20significant%20minorities%2C%20is%20very%20comparable%20to%20the%20Meitei%2C%20Kuki%20%5Band%5D%20Naga%20situation%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Absolutely.%20And%20this%20is%20where%20to%20use%20your%20evocative%20phrase%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Ca%20mixture%20of%20anarchy%20and%20civil%20war%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20we%20veer%20much%20closer%20to%20a%20situation%20that%20could%20develop%20into%20civil%20war%2C%20because%20of%20the%20complete%20separation%20of%20communities%20geographically%20and%20demographically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERG%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Absolutely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Now%2C%20the%20next%20point%20you%20make%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERG%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20And%20Karan%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESorry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERG%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20state%E2%80%99s%20inability%20or%20unwillingness%20to%20stop%20or%20stem%20this%20ethnic%20separatism%2C%20and%20its%20absolute%20refusal%20to%20do%20anything%2C%20to%20even%20begin%20a%20process%20of%20peace%20and%20reconciliation%2C%20and%20debate%20and%20dialogue%20between%20the%20warring%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Now%2C%20the%20next%20big%20point%20you%20make%20in%20that%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%20is%20to%20draw%20significant%20parallels%20between%20Manipur%20today%20and%20Gujarat%20in%202002.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20is%20with%20regard%20to%20violence%20against%20women.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20mean%20to%20be%20facile%2C%20but%20Manipur%20seems%20to%20be%20seeing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftag%2Fbilkis-bano%5C%22%3EBilkis%20Bano%3C%2Fa%3E%20repeated%20multiple%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fmanipur-video-kuki-women-stripped-manorama-bilkis-bano%5C%22%3EManipur%20Video%3A%20What%20Connects%203%20Kuki%20Women%20Stripped%2C%20Paraded%20Naked%20to%20Manorama%20and%20Bilkis%20Bano%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERG%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Well%2C%20it%20does%20appear%20so.%20I%20mean%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20never%20know%20all%20the%20details%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20very%20difficult%20for%20citizens%20and%20journalists%20and%20human%20rights%20groups%20to%20go.%20I%20mean%2C%20citizens%20groups%20that%20have%20been%20gone%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-violence-fir-fact-finding-team%5C%22%3Eslapped%20with%20absolutely%20vindictive%20FIRs%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20reporting%20on%20what%20they%E2%80%99ve%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20certainly%2C%20the%20attacks%20on%20women%2C%20the%20sexual%20assaults%20on%20women%2C%20the%20parading%20of%20women%20and%20the%20aiding%20of%20savage%20attacks%20on%20women%20by%20mobs%E2%80%A6%20The%20aiding%20of%20all%20this%20by%20the%20police%20and%20the%20state%20machinery%20is%20maybe%20even%20worse%20than%20what%20happened%20in%20Gujarat%20in%202002.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20But%20the%20echoes%20are%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERG%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Very%20much%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Targeting%20of%20women%20and%20the%20apparent%20complicity%20of%20the%20state%20machinery%20to%20permit%20it%20to%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERG%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Correct%2C%20very%20much%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Now%2C%20the%20second%20parallel%20between%20Manipur%20and%20Gujarat%20is%20that%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20quoting%20you%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20political%20establishment%20in%20general%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%20in%20particular%2C%20have%20taken%20the%20side%20of%20or%20been%20identified%20with%20the%20majority%20community.%20Here%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20drawing%20a%20direct%20comparison%20between%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20who%E2%80%99s%20chief%20minister%20of%20Manipur%20today%2C%20and%20Narendra%20Modi%20when%20he%20was%20chief%20minister%20of%20Gujarat%20in%202002.%20Am%20I%20right%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERG%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Yes%2C%20yes.%20Yes%2C%20certainly.%20So%2C%20if%20you%20read%20the%20reports%20coming%20out%20of%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20and%20I%E2%80%99ve%20talked%20to%20people%20who%20have%20been%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20Biren%20Singh%20thinks%20that%20the%20way%20to%20safeguard%20his%20seat%20is%20to%20present%20himself%20as%20the%20hero%20of%20the%20Meiteis.%20Just%20as%20Narendra%20Modi%20presented%20himself%20as%20the%20hero%20of%20the%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20now%2C%20if%20you%20look%20at%20that%20incident%20where%E2%80%A6%20I%20mean%2C%20and%20I%20argued%20in%20my%20article%2C%20and%20we%20may%20talk%20about%20this%20later%20in%20our%20discussion%2C%20the%20absolute%20first%20step%2C%20mandatory%20first%20step%20to%20stop%20this%20situation%20slipping%20further%20into%20civil%20war%20and%20anarchy%20is%20for%20the%20chief%20minister%20to%20resign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20you%E2%80%99ll%20remember%20the%20drama%E2%80%A6%20Actually%2C%20I%20even%20heard%20that%20Mr%20Arnab%20Goswami%20has%20called%20for%20the%20chief%20minister%20to%20resign.%20So%20this%20tells%20you%20how%20embarrassing%20the%20situation%20is.%20Even%20for%20channels%20close%20to%20the%20ruling%20regime%E2%80%A6%20He%20%5BBiren%20Singh%5D%20has%20to%20go.%20I%20mean%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20been%20complicit%2C%20irresponsible%2C%20amoral%2C%20and%20the%20lapses%20under%20his%20rule%20have%20been%20so%20shocking.%20He%20has%20to%20go.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20first%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(