20in%202002.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERG%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20And%20particularly%20not%20just%20in%20the%E2%80%A6%20In%202002%2C%20it%20happened%20to%20some%20extent%20in%20the%20riots%2C%20and%20much%20more%20visibly%20in%20the%20elections%20that%20followed.%20Now%2C%20is%20this%20Biren%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20calculation%3F%20I%20mean%2C%20one%20must%20ask%20that%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Now%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20sections%20of%20that%20article%20you%20wrote%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20when%20you%20ask%20the%20question%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20is%20Biren%20Singh%20still%20in%20office%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20seems%20you%20have%20three%20answers%20and%20I%20want%20to%20go%20through%20each%20of%20them%20one%20by%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%20you%20say%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20quoting%20you%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20important%20reason%20that%20Biren%20Singh%20remains%20in%20office%20is%20the%20Modi%20regime%E2%80%99s%20absolute%20refusal%20to%20admit%20that%20they%20have%20ever%20been%20at%20fault.%E2%80%9D%20I%20think%20I%20understand%20what%20you%E2%80%99re%20saying%2C%20but%20could%20you%20explain%20it%20more%20fully%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERG%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Yeah.%20So%20they%20have%20to%20be%20presented%20by%20their%20spin%20masters%2C%20by%20their%20ministers%2C%20as%20flawless.%20So%20they%E2%80%99ve%20never%20accounted%20for%20the%20horrible%20disaster%20of%20demonetisation%20from%20which%20our%20economy%20has%20not%20recovered.%20%5BFor%5D%20the%20mishandling%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20particularly%20the%20arbitrary%20lockdown.%20For%20the%20transgression%20into%20what%20is%20estimated%20to%20be%20several%20thousand%20kilometres%20of%20our%20territory%20by%20Chinese%20troops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20they%20can%20never%20make%20a%20mistake%2C%20and%20even%20a%20mistake%20that%20costs%20the%20country%20and%20its%20people%20and%20its%20institutions%20and%20its%20stability%20dearly.%20So%20this%20is%20of%20a%20pattern.%20Because%20in%20this%20case%2C%20as%20I%20say%20also%20in%20my%20article%2C%20before%20an%20election%20they%20may%20decide%2C%20I%20think%20Gujarat%2C%20you%20know%2C%20recently%2C%20that%20the%20incumbent%20chief%20minister%2C%20Mr%20Vijay%20Rupani%20is%20not%20going%20to%20win%20them%20re-election%2C%20so%20they%20replace%20him%20with%20someone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20this%20is%20very%20different.%20This%20is%20a%20situation%20of%2C%20to%20repeat%20the%20phrase%2C%20anarchy%20going%20towards%20%E2%80%93%20not%20yet%20%E2%80%93%20but%20a%20state%20of%20the%20Union%20going%20towards%20anarchy%20and%20civil%20war%2C%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%20aiding%20in%20this%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight.%20Now%2C%20with%20hundreds%20dead%2C%20many%20women%20raped%2C%20an%20estimated%2060%2C000%20displaced%2C%20a%20complete%20separation%20%E2%80%93%20territorial%20and%20ethnic%20separation%20%E2%80%93%20of%20the%20state%2C%20and%20you%20haven%E2%80%99t%20dismissed%20him.%20And%20why%20not%3F%20Because%20you%20cannot%20admit%20%E2%80%93%20there%20may%20be%20other%20reasons%2C%20and%20we%20can%20talk%20about%20that%20%E2%80%93%20but%20essentially%20one%20reason%20is%20the%20BJP%20can%20never%20admit%20to%20having%20made%20a%20mistake.%20Which%20is%20shocking%20in%20a%20democracy%2C%20because%20you%20must%20be%20accountable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-violence-reasons-failure-and-solution-q-and-a%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20Behind%20the%20Manipur%20Violence%20and%20Why%20Stopping%20It%20Poses%20a%20Test%20For%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20mean%2C%20to%20the%20credit%20of%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20when%20there%20were%20credible%20accusations%20against%20one%20or%20two%20of%20his%20ministers%2C%20he%20dismissed%20them%2C%20you%20know%3F%20And%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cyou%20fight%20in%20the%20courts%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20it%20appears%20that%20these%20accusations%20are%20reasonably%20credible%20%E2%80%93%20and%20they%20were%20senior%20cabinet%20ministers%20%E2%80%93%20and%20they%20went%E2%80%A6%20including%20not%20just%20from%20the%20alliance%2C%20but%20even%20from%20the%20Congress%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20there%20was%2C%20for%20example%2C%20the%20attack%20on%20Mumbai%20in%202008%2C%20the%20home%20minister%20was%20replaced.%20Mr%20Shivraj%20Patil%20was%20held%20accountable%20and%20replaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20in%20any%20democracy%20we%20do%20this%2C%20especially%2C%20if%20the%20error%20or%20the%20costs%20of%20this%20error%20are%20so%E2%80%A6%20if%20the%20error%20is%20so%20egregious%20and%20the%20human%20costs%20of%20this%20error%20are%20so%20enormous%2C%20as%20is%20the%20case%20with%20Biren%20Singh%20and%20his%20maladministration%20of%20the%20state%20of%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Quite%20right.%20The%20BJP%20believes%E2%80%A6%20as%20a%20party%2C%20it%20believes%20that%20its%20chief%20ministers%20as%20institutions%20are%20infallible%2C%20they%20cannot%20be%20replaced%20because%20the%20admission%20of%20a%20mistake%20would%20shatter%20that%20claim%20to%20infallibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20reason%20why%20you%20believe%20Biren%20Singh%20has%20not%20been%20removed%20comes%20a%20lot%20closer%20to%20the%20bone.%20You%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20may%20lead%20to%20calls%20for%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20to%20resign%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%20In%20other%20words%2C%20retaining%20Biren%20Singh%20is%20a%20shield%20to%20protect%20Amit%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERG%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Well%2C%20it%20could%20be%20right.%20Though%2C%20if%20Amit%20Shah%20is%20canny%20and%20pragmatic%2C%20he%20could%20sacrifice%20Biren%20Singh%20and%20try%20to%20save%20his%20own%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20let%20me%20just%20say%20this%2C%20that%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20own%20conduct%20as%20home%20minister%20in%20this%20particular%20case%2C%20has%20not%20been%20salutary.%20Nor%20in%20other%20cases.%20I%20mean%2C%20if%20you%20think%20of%20the%20Delhi%20riots%20that%20happened%20when%20the%20American%20president%20no%20less%20was%20visiting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20they%20happened%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20in%20the%20controlling%20of%20those%20riots%2C%20Muslims%20were%20gone%20after%20disproportionately%20%E2%80%93%20many%20more%20cases%20were%20launched%20against%20them%2C%20and%20there%20was%20a%20clear%20bias%20in%20the%20way%20the%20Delhi%20police%2C%20which%20operates%20again%20under%20Mr%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20operated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fpolice-witness-not-credible-callous-probe-how-the-delhi-riots-cases-have-evolved%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Police%20Witness%20Not%20Credible%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Callous%20Probe%E2%80%99%3A%20How%20the%20Delhi%20Riots%20Cases%20Have%20Evolved%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20look%20at%20more%20recently%2C%20in%20my%20home%20state%20of%20Karnataka%E2%80%A6%20The%20troubles%20in%20Manipur%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fnortheast-meitei-st-demand-manipur-hc-8581664%2F%5C%22%3Estarted%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20April%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20by%20early%20May%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmanipur-violence-deaths%5C%22%3Eclear%20that%20this%20is%20a%20serious%20issue%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20Kukis%20and%20Meiteis%20are%20becoming%20implacable%20enemies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20does%20Mr%20Amit%20Shah%20do%3F%20He%20comes%20to%20my%20home%20state%2C%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20tries%20to%20polarise%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims.%20That%20was%20the%20burden%20of%20his%20electoral%20campaign%20even%20when%20there%20is%20an%20ethnic%20conflict%20emerging%20and%20assuming%20serious%20proportions%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20look%20at%20Delhi.%20Look%20at%20Karnataka.%20Then%20look%20at%20Manipur%20itself.%20I%20mean%2C%20he%20made%20a%20brief%20visit%20there%2C%20and%20he%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20gone%20back.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Famit-shah-manipur-promises-betrayed%5C%22%3EHe%20promised%20he%E2%80%99d%20be%20back%20in%2015%20days.%3C%2Fa%3E%20You%20know%2C%20if%20you%20look%20at%20law%20and%20order%20under%20him%2C%20all%20kinds%20of%20spin%20was%20portrayed%2C%20that%20the%20Kukis%20are%20actually%20foreigners%2C%20migrants%2C%20and%20the%20chief%20of%20defence%20staff%20had%20to%20dispel%20that%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%98No%2C%20this%20is%20an%20internal%20issue.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20if%20you%20look%20at%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20home%20minister%2C%20in%20this%20particular%20case%20and%20in%20other%20cases%20in%20the%20past%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20very%2C%20you%20know%2C%20encouraging.%20He%E2%80%99s%20a%20person%20who%20seems%20to%20thrive%20on%20disunity%20and%20division%20and%20discord%20because%20he%20sees%20in%20that%20a%20route%20to%20a%20consolidation%20of%20a%20Hindu%20majority%20at%20election%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Then%20let%20me%20ask%20you%20bluntly%2C%20has%20the%20time%20come%20for%20Amit%20Shah%20to%20resign%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERG%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20mean%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%E2%80%A6%20I%20mean%2C%20I%20am%20in%20no%20position%20to%20ask%20him%20to%20resign%2C%20let%20alone%2C%20you%20know%2C%20influence%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20let%E2%80%99s%20say%20that%20if%20you%20look%20at%20the%20history%20of%20home%20ministers%20since%201947%20%E2%80%93%20when%20we%20became%20independent%20%E2%80%93%20till%202023%2C%20and%20you%20placed%20him%20on%20a%20spectrum%2C%20Sardar%20Patel%20is%20at%20one%20end%20of%20the%20spectrum%20and%20Amit%20Shah%20close%20to%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20spectrum.%20As%20a%20historian%2C%20I%20will%20just%20pass%20this%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Okay.%20The%20third%20reason%20mentioned%20in%20your%20article%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20why%20Biren%20Singh%20remains%20in%20office%2C%20is%20because%20%E2%80%93%20and%20again%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20quoting%20you%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9CThe%20sacking%20of%20the%20present%20chief%20minister%20of%20Manipur%20would%20raise%20afresh%20uncomfortable%20questions%20about%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20BJP%20to%20sack%20the%20Gujarat%20chief%20minister%20after%20the%20riots%20of%202002.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20Biren%20Singh%20is%20also%20being%20retained%20to%20protect%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERG%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Well%2C%20it%20appears%20so.%20I%20mean%2C%20the%20parallels%20are%20%5Binaudible%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20me%20say%20this%2C%20that%20in%202002%E2%80%A6%20You%20see%2C%20Karan%2C%20let%20me%20tell%20you%20something.%20Any%20inter-communal%20riot%20can%20be%20stopped%20from%20escalating%20if%20the%20chief%20minister%20or%20the%20home%20minister%20intervenes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20227px)%2085vw%2C%20227px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F14140203%2F1200px-Jyoti_Basu_-_Calcutta_1996-12-21_089_Cropped-227x300.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22227%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F14140203%2F1200px-Jyoti_Basu_-_Calcutta_1996-12-21_089_Cropped-227x300.jpg%20227w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F14140203%2F1200px-Jyoti_Basu_-_Calcutta_1996-12-21_089_Cropped-774x1024.jpg%20774w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F14140203%2F1200px-Jyoti_Basu_-_Calcutta_1996-12-21_089_Cropped.jpg%20907w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-290115%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJyoti%20Basu.%20Credit%3A%20Biswarup%20Ganguly%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20CC%20BY-3.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20in%20Kolkata%20in%201984%20when%20Mrs%20%5BIndira%5D%20Gandhi%20was%20assassinated.%20The%2050%2C000%20Sikhs%20in%20Kolkata%20were%20then%20mostly%20driving%20taxis%20and%20identified%20by%20their%20turbans.%20Jyoti%20Basu%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNot%20one%20will%20be%20harmed%E2%80%9D.%20And%20they%20were%20not.%20So%20his%20behaviour%20was%20in%20absolute%20contrast%20to%20that%20of%20Narasimha%20Rao%2C%20who%20was%20home%20minister%2C%20and%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20had%20just%20come%20in%20as%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20similarly%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20there%20have%20been%20instances%20where%20there%20have%20been%20brave%20chief%20ministers.%20J.H.%20Patel%20of%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20was%20not%20a%20great%20chief%20minister%2C%20but%20he%20stopped%20a%20major%20communal%20conflagration%20by%20sending%2010%2C000%20troops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20in%202002%2C%20if%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20acted%20the%20way%20Jyoti%20Basu%20had%20in%201984%2C%20the%20riots%20would%20not%20have%20escalated%20in%20the%20way%20they%20did%2C%20and%20the%20widespread%20programme%20against%20Muslims%20%E2%80%93%20which%20reached%20deep%20into%20the%20countryside%20across%20many%20districts%20of%20Gujarat%20%E2%80%93%20would%20not%20have%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20may%20still%20have%20been%20a%20few%20stray%20incidents%20because%20the%20state%20is%20not%20omnipresent%20and%20omnipotent%2C%20but%20it%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20achieved%20this%20pogrom-like%20character.%20So%20his%20conduct%20was%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20he%20failed%20in%20his%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20is%20why%2C%20first%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%2C%20went%20to%20Gujarat%2C%20visited%20the%20refugee%20camps.%20When%20he%20saw%20the%20pitiable%20condition%20of%20the%20refugees%2C%20mostly%20Muslim%20refugees%2C%20he%20chastised%20the%20chief%20minister%20for%20his%20lack%20of%20%3Cem%3Erajdharma%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20of%20course%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20sack%20him%2C%20and%20as%20I%20say%20in%20my%20article%2C%20he%20was%20overruled%20by%20other%20members%20of%20his%20party%2C%20such%20as%20L.K.%20Advani%20and%20Arun%20Jaitley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20in%20that%20sense%2C%20here%2C%20because%20of%20what%20happened%20in%202002%2C%20forget%20the%20question%E2%80%A6%20Well%2C%20I%20still%20wish%20and%20hope%20that%20Biren%20Singh%20is%20sacked%2C%20because%20that%20would%20be%20the%20first%20step%E2%80%A6%20Karan%2C%20this%20is%20a%20state%20of%20our%20union%20in%20a%20deeply%20divided%20and%20fragile%20condition.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20border%20state%20with%20a%20history%20of%20insurgency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlready%20there%20have%20been%20spillover%20effects%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fmizoram-seeks-5-crore-central-aid-for-relief-to-displaced-people-from-violence-hit-manipur%2Farticle66911849.ece%5C%22%3EMizoram%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fensure-manipur-refugees-return-meghalaya-tribal-council-tells-traditional-local-bodies%2Farticle67014972.ece%5C%22%3EMeghalaya%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%E2%80%99s%20happened.%20This%20conflict%20has%20spilled%20over%20and%20those%20are%20all%20border%20states.%20We%20live%20in%20a%20very%20hostile%20and%20troubled%20neighbourhood.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20good%20relations%20with%20most%20of%20our%20neighbours%2C%20our%20international%20neighbours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20clearly%2C%20even%20now%2C%20as%20an%20Indian%20citizen%2C%20as%20a%20democrat%20who%20bears%20no%20party%20affiliation%2C%20I%20would%20want%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20sack%20Biren%20Singh.%20That%20should%20be%20the%20first%20step.%20Now%20he%20has%20not%20done%20it.%20And%20maybe%20because%20of%20what%20happened%20in%202002%2C%20he%20can%E2%80%99t%20even%20remind%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20his%20rajdharma.%20So%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20parallels%20run%20very%20close%20to%20the%20bone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-manipur-gujarat%5C%22%3EIt%20Is%20Naive%20to%20Expect%20PM%20Modi%20to%20Speak%20up%20During%20Crises%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Absolutely%2C%20and%20as%20you%20say%2C%20were%20Biren%20Singh%20to%20be%20sacked%20%E2%80%93%20unlikely%20though%20it%20seems%20at%20the%20moment%20%E2%80%93%20those%20uncomfortable%20questions%20about%202002%2C%20when%20Modi%20was%20chief%20minister%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20would%20be%20once%20again%20questions%20that%20he%20would%20have%20to%20face%20as%20prime%20minister%2C%20and%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERG%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20slightly%20disagree%20with%20you%2C%20Karan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20But%20I%E2%80%99m%20quoting%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERG%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20No%2C%20I%20slightly%20disagree%20with%20you%2C%20because%20he%20could%20still%20sack%20him%2C%20in%20that%20human%20beings%20grow.%20You%20know%2C%20they%20grow%20intellectually%2C%20they%20expand%20their%20knowledge%20base%2C%20they%20learn%20the%20virtues%20of%20contrition.%20Maybe%20their%20conscience%20can%20develop%20a%20little%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20to%20sack%20Biren%20Singh%20today%20and%20recognise%20his%20failures%20%E2%80%93%20his%20administrative%20failures%20and%20his%20failures%20to%20be%20impartial%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20identifies%20with%20the%20majority%20community%20or%20the%20dominant%20community%20in%20Manipur%2C%20he%20would%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20know%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20a%20biographer%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20and%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20believed%20that%20even%2C%20you%20know%2C%20mobsters%20and%20gangsters%20could%20redeem%20themselves.%20So%20absolutely%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20hold%20Modi%20to%20what%20happened%20completely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20historian%2C%20I%20will%20draw%20the%20parallels%20between%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20Manipur%20today%20and%20what%20happened%20in%202002.%20Those%20are%20historical%20parallels%20I%20draw%20as%20a%20scholar.%20As%20a%20citizen%2C%20I%20would%20still%20want%20my%20prime%20minister%20to%20sack%20the%20Manipur%20chief%20minister%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20And%20this%20is%20a%20very%20interesting%20development%20in%20your%20thinking.%20Between%20the%20article%20you%20wrote%20yesterday%20and%20the%20interview%20you%E2%80%99re%20giving%20today%2C%20you%20believe%20that%20Mr%20Modi%20would%20show%20signs%20of%20growth%2C%20actually%20signs%20of%20having%20learned%2C%20if%20he%20were%20to%20sack%20Biren%20Singh%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERG%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Yes.%20Contrition%2C%20moral%20growth%2C%20some%20sense%20of%20atonement%2C%20some%20regard%20for%20how%20serious%20the%20situation%20is%2C%20some%20diluting%20of%20his%20ego%20and%20his%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20as%20a%20human%20being%2C%20he%20would%20be%20better%20and%20the%20country%20would%20be%20better.%20And%20Manipur%20would%20be%E2%80%A6%20at%20least%20could%20think%20of%20peace%20and%20reconciliation%20and%20safety%20for%20its%20women%20if%20Biren%20Singh%20was%20sacked%20by%20Narendra%20Modi%20any%20time%20soon.%20Today%2C%20tomorrow%2C%20next%20week%2C%20whatever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20But%20let%20me%20put%20this%20to%20you.%20I%20get%20the%20feeling%20from%20what%20you%E2%80%99ve%20said%20and%20the%20way%20your%20thinking%20has%20evolved%20in%20the%20last%2024%20hours%2C%20that%20what%20I%20thought%20was%20your%20conclusion%20in%20your%20article%20about%20Biren%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20position%20and%20the%20need%20to%20retain%20him%20may%20not%20be%20your%20position%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20me%20read%20it%20out.%20And%20then%20you%20tell%20me.%20I%E2%80%99ll%20read%20it%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20parallels%20between%20Gujarat%20then%20and%20Manipur%20now%20run%20ever%20so%20close%20to%20the%20bone.%20Because%20of%20his%20own%20complicated%20past%2C%20the%20current%20prime%20minister%20cannot%20ask%20for%20the%20replacement%20of%20the%20Manipur%20chief%20minister.%20He%20cannot%20even%20ask%20him%20to%20practise%20his%20rajdharma.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20you%20believe%2C%20that%20were%20he%20to%20sack%20him%2C%20he%20would%20show%20moral%20growth.%20Modi%20would%20show%20that%20he%20has%20grown%20morally%2C%20he%20has%20learnt%20administratively%20and%20be%20a%20better%20government%20official%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERG%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Of%20course.%20And%20the%20fact%20is%2C%20I%20%5Binaudible%5D%20I%20mean%2C%20I%20wrote%20the%20piece%2C%20actually%2C%20on%20Sunday.%20It%20was%20published%20on%20Monday%20morning.%20As%20I%20said%2C%20even%20television%20channels%20extremely%20sympathetic%20%5Bto%20and%5D%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20cheerleaders%20for%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20have%20recognised%20that%20the%20first%20step%20in%20any%20damage%20control%20would%20be%20this.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpiyush-goyal-says-govt-will-discuss-manipur-in-parliament-at-2-pm-opposition-firm-on-modi-statement%5C%22%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20been%20asking%20for%20it.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F31120639%2FF2V12XeXIAEO3aY-1024x461.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%2