r%20customers.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20statement%20was%20addressed%20to%20shareholders%20on%20account%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dob8_rPryPgE%5C%22%3Evideo%3C%2Fa%3E%20(in%20Bengali%20with%20English%20subtitles)%20of%20an%20HDFC%20Bank%20zonal%20head%20exhibiting%20toxic%20behaviour%20with%20his%20team%20going%20viral%20soon%20after%20its%20release%20on%20June%205%2C%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMDahariya%2Fstatus%2F1665561179429773321%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3ETwitter%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20the%20video%2C%20the%20zonal%20head%20is%20seen%20berating%20his%20junior%20staff%20for%20not%20meeting%20the%20aggressive%20targets.%20Some%20hours%20later%2C%20HDFC%20Bank%20responded%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fhdfc-bank-suspends-officer-for-unruly-behaviour-with-colleagues-10745551.html%5C%22%3Esuspending%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20concerned%20official%20and%20launching%20an%20investigation%20against%20him%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20bank%20has%20zero%20tolerance%20for%20such%20behaviour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20toxic%20work%20culture%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20short%20video%20obviously%20indicates%20the%20toxic%20work%20culture%20in%20the%20financial%20sector.%20But%20it%20is%20also%20symptomatic%20of%20larger%20issues%20in%20the%20sector%2C%20such%20as%20setting%20unrealistic%20sales%20targets%2C%20poor%20leadership%20development%2C%20and%20lack%20of%20communication%20and%20motivational%20skills.%20These%20factors%20are%20not%20always%20publicly%20discussed%20by%20the%20senior%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20course%20of%20the%20video%2C%20viewers%20get%20to%20see%20the%20faces%20of%20the%20other%20participants%20on%20the%20call%2C%20including%20the%20individuals%20who%20are%20the%20victims%20of%20the%20official%E2%80%99s%20verbal%20abuse.%20At%20no%20time%20do%20they%20exhibit%20surprise%20at%20such%20toxic%20behaviour%2C%20which%20indicates%20two%20things%3A%20either%20these%20individuals%20can%20disguise%20their%20emotions%20or%20that%20the%20official%20is%20a%20repeat%20offender%20and%20they%20are%20used%20to%20such%20behaviour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20unauthorised%20recording%20of%20the%20video%20conference%20indicates%20that%20someone%20wanted%20to%20document%20the%20habitual%20misbehaviour%20of%20the%20concerned%20official%2C%20in%20order%20to%20report%20it%20to%20the%20senior%20authorities.%20Normally%2C%20such%20sales%20review%20conference%20calls%20last%20for%20one%20to%20two%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20some%20allege%20that%20the%20manager%20exhibited%20such%20behaviour%20for%20a%20short%20time%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20his%20behaviour%20was%20so%20obnoxious%20even%20for%20that%20short%20duration%20is%20inexcusable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20pertinent%20to%20note%20that%20the%20zonal%20head%20is%20addressing%20experienced%20mid-management%20employees%20having%20eight%20to%2015%20years%20of%20experience%2C%20who%20are%20either%20in%20charge%20of%20clusters%20(branches%20report%20to%20a%20cluster%20head)%20or%20are%20senior%20branch%20managers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20performance-driven%20company%2C%20the%20management%20has%20the%20right%20to%20give%20stretched%20targets%2C%20but%20the%20employees%20also%20have%20the%20right%20to%20demand%20enablers%20such%20as%20additional%20human%20resources%2C%20client%20databases%2C%20technology%20assistance%2C%20multiple%20channels%2C%20etc.%20In%20the%20process%20of%20negotiation%20between%20the%20leader%20and%20the%20staff%2C%20achievable%2C%20or%20even%20slightly%20stretched%2C%20targets%20can%20be%20set%20and%20the%20enablers%20provided%20to%20achieve%20those%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20HDFC%20Bank%20is%20a%20high-performance-oriented%20bank%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20the%20management%20may%20be%20setting%20unrealistic%20sales%20targets%20without%20providing%20the%20required%20enablers%2C%20and%20that%20targets%20are%20set%20without%20taking%20inputs%20from%20the%20ground%20level%20on%20what%20is%20achievable%20with%20the%20given%20enablers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20leader%E2%80%99s%20responsibility%20to%20provide%20the%20strategy%20and%20guide%20the%20juniors%20on%20how%20the%20targets%20can%20be%20met%2C%20and%20how%20to%20adopt%20different%20methods%20when%20the%20initial%20methods%20are%20not%20producing%20results.%20However%2C%20the%20entire%20video%20is%20a%20monologue%2C%20in%20which%20the%20official%20is%20simply%20berating%20his%20juniors%20for%20not%20achieving%20the%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3kXcP8ystpg%5C%22%3Eanother%3C%2Fa%3E%20video%20of%20the%20same%20meeting%2C%20there%20is%2C%20briefly%2C%20a%20rare%20commendation%20by%20the%20zonal%20head%20to%20one%20of%20his%20juniors%2C%20but%20the%20general%20tenor%20of%20the%20video%20is%20the%20same.%20There%20is%20no%20dialogue%20between%20the%20leader%20and%20his%20juniors%20regarding%20the%20problems%20that%20they%20may%20be%20facing%2C%20nor%20is%20the%20leader%20providing%20any%20enablers%20and%2For%20solutions.%20There%20is%20a%20complete%20absence%20of%20strategy%20and%20mentoring%20in%20the%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20communication%20training%20on%20how%20leaders%20should%20speak%20and%20conduct%20themselves%20in%20a%20group%20environment%20is%20also%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaising%20one%E2%80%99s%20voice%2C%20shouting%2C%20and%20threatening%20to%20sack%20the%20concerned%20employee%20appear%20to%20be%20accepted%20practices%20for%20leaders%20to%20communicate%20with%20their%20junior%20employees%20who%20are%20failing%20to%20meet%20targets.%20The%20fear%20culture%20is%20a%20primitive%20form%20of%20pressure%20put%20on%20mid%20and%20senior%20level%20executives%20in%20any%20organisation.%20It%20is%20possible%20that%20when%20the%20junior%20employees%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20seniors%20who%20abuse%20and%20terrorise%20in%20order%20to%20achieve%20targets%2C%20they%20in%20turn%2C%20upon%20being%20promoted%2C%20employ%20the%20same%20tools%20on%20their%20junior%20employees.%20This%20indicates%20that%20they%2C%20indeed%2C%20know%20no%20other%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20company%2C%20and%20in%20particular%2C%20the%20human%20resources%20department%2C%20to%20groom%20leaders%20and%20supervisors%20and%20impart%20the%20necessary%20knowledge%2C%20motivational%20and%20communication%20skills%20in%20managing%20individuals%20to%20grow%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conduct%20of%20this%20zonal%20head%20in%20the%20video%20conference%20call%20reveals%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20organisation%20in%20selection%20and%20training%20of%20its%20leaders.%20Such%20conduct%20is%20reportedly%20widespread%20in%20the%20financial%20sector%20as%20another%20excessively%20abusive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fpratyay-banerjee-4a512a116_leadership-employment-india-activity-7083121780118224896-RlDD%2F%3Futm_source%3Dshare%26utm_medium%3Dmember_desktop%5C%22%3Evideo%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20a%20Bajaj%20Financial%20Services%20manager%20reaffirms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20the%20industry%20has%20failed%20in%20a%20big%20way%20in%20equipping%20leaders%20with%20the%20all-important%20soft%20skills%20of%20leadership%2C%20mentoring%20and%20communication%20to%20develop%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20extremely%20important%20for%20leaders%20to%20be%20instructed%20on%20how%20to%20calibrate%20pressure%3B%20too%20little%20may%20lead%20to%20complacency%2C%20too%20much%20may%20cause%20a%20demoralised%20workforce%2C%20labour%20unrest%2C%20and%20attrition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Fhigh-attrition-rate-at-kotak-mahindra-bank-fails-to-find-a-spot-in-annual-report%5C%22%3EThe%20Issue%20of%20High%20Attrition%20Rate%20at%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%20Fails%20to%20Find%20a%20Spot%20in%20Annual%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERising%20attrition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrivate%20sector%20banks%20like%20HDFC%20Bank%2C%20Axis%20Bank%2C%20and%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%20(KMB)%20have%20a%20significantly%20higher%20staff%20attrition%20at%20around%2034%25%20to%2046%25%2C%20as%20compared%20with%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20at%204.7%25%2C%20which%20is%20a%20performance-driven%20government%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EICICI%20Bank%20has%20not%20disclosed%20its%20numbers%20on%20attrition%20till%20FY22.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20SBI%20having%20a%20significantly%20larger%20staff%2C%20its%20attrition%20in%20absolute%20numbers%20too%20is%20much%20lower%20than%20HDFC%20Bank%2C%20Axis%20Bank%20and%20KMB.%20While%20the%20setting%20and%20achieving%20of%20sales%20targets%20is%20lower%20in%20government%20banks%2C%20the%20difference%20in%20attrition%20is%20huge%2C%20which%20can%20be%20partly%20explained%20by%20private%20banks%E2%80%99%20more%20aggressive%20work%20culture%20and%20inadequate%20training%20in%20developing%20leadership%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F31134932%2Fimage-1184.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F31134932%2Fimage-1184.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F31134932%2Fimage-1184-300x82.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F31134932%2Fimage-1184-1024x280.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665967%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22328%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20Banks%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELabour%20unions%20and%20officer%20associations%20are%20institutional%20mechanisms%20protecting%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20staff.%20Having%20such%20organisations%20insulates%20the%20lower%20level%20staff%20from%20the%20excesses%20of%20the%20senior%20management%2C%20and%20curtails%20rude%20behaviour%20and%20long%20working%20hours.%20It%2C%20therefore%2C%20comes%20as%20no%20surprise%20that%20organisations%20experiencing%20a%20high%20attrition%20rate%20often%20lack%20any%20significant%20unions%20or%20officer%20associations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20is%20the%20case%20with%20HDFC%20Bank%2C%20Axis%20Bank%2C%20KMB%20and%20Yes%20Bank%20whereas%20at%20SBI%2C%2096.2%25%20of%20the%20permanent%20workforce%20in%20FY23%20were%20members%20of%20such%20unions%20and%20officer%20associations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20increasing%20competition%20from%20other%20banks%2C%20non-bank%20finance%20companies%20and%20financial%20technology%20companies%2C%20there%20may%20be%20tremendous%20pressure%20on%20the%20companies%20to%20grow%20and%20enhance%20their%20valuation.%20Unfortunately%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20the%20management%E2%80%99s%20perception%20is%20limited%20to%20utilising%20aggressive%20tactics%20such%20as%20shouting%2C%20abusing%2C%20and%20threatening%20to%20terminate%20lower-level%20staff%20to%20meet%20over-ambitious%20sales%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20social%20media%20users%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fsearch%2Fresults%2Fall%2F%3Fkeywords%3Dpushpal%2520roy%26origin%3DGLOBAL_SEARCH_HEADER%26sid%3D0jk%5C%22%3Ehave%20commented%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20such%20behaviour%20is%20common%20in%20the%20private%20financial%20sector%2C%20where%20employees%20face%20relentless%20pressure%20to%20meet%20multiple%20product%20targets%20such%20as%20current%2C%20savings%20and%20term%20deposits%2C%20insurance%2C%20mutual%20funds%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20writer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Fmore-than-a-third-of-the-axis-bank-staff-quit-in-fy2023-reveals-annual-report%5C%22%3Ehad%20highlighted%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20example%20of%20Ravi%20Narayanan%2C%20group%20head%20%E2%80%93%20retail%20liabilities%20and%20branch%20banking%2C%20Axis%20Bank%2C%20who%20had%20conducted%20a%20town%20hall%20meeting%20for%20the%20staff%20on%20December%2024%2C%202021.%20Narayanan%20held%20a%20position%20just%20one%20level%20below%20the%20board%20of%20directors.%20In%20the%20town%20hall%20meeting%20he%20had%20reportedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhemindrahazari.com%2F2022%2F01%2F10%2Faxis-banks-toxic-call-to-staff-to-fight-abuse-and-undermine-one-another-in-pursuit-of-business%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEmployees%20should%20fight%2C%20abuse%20and%20complain%20amongst%20them%20%5B%3Cem%3Esic%3C%2Fem%3E%5D%20for%20business%2C%20this%20is%20the%20attitude%20what%20%5B%3Cem%3Esic%3C%2Fem%3E%5D%20I%20like.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20recent%20Town%20Hall%20meet%2C%20my%20friend%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frave9007%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40rave9007%3C%2Fa%3E%20Country%20Head%2C%20Branch%20Banking%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAxisBank%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40AxisBank%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20quoting%2C%20%E2%80%9C%20employees%20should%20fight%2C%20abuse%20and%20complain%20amongst%20them%20for%20business%2C%20this%20is%20the%20attitude%20what%20i%20like%E2%80%9D.%20Seriously%20what%20type%20of%20toxicity%20is%20flowing%20resulting%20in%20the%20attrition%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F5Gd51L98fK%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F5Gd51L98fK%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20MDahariya1%20%E2%80%93%20my%20original%20a%2Fc%20unsuspended%20now%20(%40MDahariya1)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMDahariya1%2Fstatus%2F1476816255956885506%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2031%2C%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20the%20far%20less%20senior%20HDFC%20Bank%20official%2C%20who%20was%20immediately%20suspended%20by%20the%20bank%2C%20Narayanan%20continues%20to%20occupy%20his%20post%20at%20Axis%20Bank.%20This%20indicates%20that%20mid-level%20managers%20in%20the%20financial%20sector%20are%20expendable%2C%20while%20higher-ranking%20officials%20enjoy%20a%20degree%20of%20protection%20even%20when%20involved%20in%20toxic%20behaviour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Fmore-than-a-third-of-the-axis-bank-staff-quit-in-fy2023-reveals-annual-report%5C%22%3EMore%20Than%20a%20Third%20of%20the%20Axis%20Bank%20Staff%20Quit%20in%20FY2023%2C%20Reveals%20Annual%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20a%20screenshot%20of%20some%20responses%20posted%20by%20LinkedIn%20users%20on%20the%20problem%20of%20the%20widely%20prevalent%20abuse%20culture%20in%20the%20sector.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F31145343%2Fimage-1186.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22608%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F31145343%2Fimage-1186.png%20608w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F31145343%2Fimage-1186-222x300.png%20222w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665973%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22822%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20a%20screenshot%20of%20some%20responses%20posted%20by%20LinkedIn%20users%20on%20the%20problem%20of%20the%20widely%20prevalent%20abuse%20culture%20in%20the%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20much-needed%20measures%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20the%20banking%20regulator%20must%20intervene%20and%20conduct%20its%20own%20investigation%20to%20determine%20how%20widespread%20this%20toxic%20culture%20is%2C%20and%20whether%20senior%20management%20is%20setting%20unrealistically%20high%20sales%20targets%2C%20which%20results%20in%20such%20behaviour%20and%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20that%20the%20human%20resources%20department%20is%20empowered%20by%20the%20board%20of%20directors%20and%20by%20the%20CEO%20to%20insulate%20staff%20in%20high%20performance%20companies%20from%20such%20toxic%20pressures.%20It%20must%20educate%20staff%20in%20motivational%2C%20communication%20and%20leadership%20skills.%20The%20management%20should%20take%20a%20firm%20stance%20to%20eradicate%20such%20a%20toxic%20work%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20regulator%20must%20also%20consider%20insisting%20on%20the%20establishment%20of%20labour%20unions%20and%20officer%20associations%20in%20private%20sector%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20this%20culture%20results%20in%20mis-selling%20to%20the%20banks%E2%80%99%20own%20customers%2C%20eroding%20trust%20and%20confidence%2C%20the%20banking%20regulator%20must%20consider%20taking%20some%20serious%20measures%20such%20as%20prohibiting%20banks%20from%20engaging%20in%20third-party%20sales%20or%20enforcing%20punitive%20penalties%20for%20mis-selling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20such%20abusive%20behaviour%20%E2%80%93%20as%20seen%20in%20the%20viral%20videos%20from%20HDFC%20Bank%20and%20Bajaj%20Financial%20Services%20managers%20%E2%80%93%20is%20common%20in%20the%20financial%20sector%2C%20the%20stock%20market%20has%20treated%20the%20incidents%20as%20a%20one-off%20event%20which%20will%20not%20impact%20the%20financial%20sector.%20The%20stock%20market%20does%20not%20contemplate%20any%20major%20fallout%20from%20this%20issue%2C%20and%20normally%2C%20the%20senior%20management%20responds%20by%20saying%20that%20these%20are%20isolated%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20culture%20where%20CEOs%20seldom%20publicly%20acknowledge%20any%20shortcomings%2C%20Sashidhar%20Jagdishan%E2%80%99s%20candor%20with%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20shareholders%20is%20commendable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20na%C3%AFve%20on%20the%20part%20of%20stakeholders%20and%20the%20financial%20sector%20regulator%20to%20perceive%20these%20incidents%20as%20isolated%2C%20or%20merely%20cases%20of%20a%20few%20bad%20apples.%20The%20banking%20industry%20holds%20strategic%20importance%20in%20the%20economy%20and%20employs%20a%20large%20labour%20force.%20It%20cannot%20overlook%20the%20repercussions%20of%20an%20oppressed%2C%20disgruntled%20labour%20force%2C%20which%20is%20forced%20into%20mis-selling%20to%20achieve%20unrealistic%20sales%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EHemindra%20Hazari%20is%20a%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20registered%20independent%20research%20analyst%3C%2Fi%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDISCLOSURE%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%2C%20Hemindra%20Hazari%2C%20am%20a%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20registered%20independent%20research%20analyst%20(Regd.%20No.%20INH000000594).%20%3Cstrong%3EI%20own%20equity%20shares%20in%20all%20the%20companies%20mentioned%20in%20this%20report%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%3Cstrong%3EHDFC%20Bank%20subscribes%20to%20this%20analyst%E2%80%99s%20research%20and%20a%20member%20of%20this%20analyst%E2%80%99s%20family%20is%20employed%20with%20the%20bank%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20Views%20expressed%20in%20this%20Insight%20accurately%20reflect%20my%20personal%20opinion%20about%20the%20referenced%20securities%20and%20issuers%20and%2For%20other%20subject%20matter%20as%20appropriate.%20This%20Insight%20does%20not%20contain%20and%20is%20not%20based%20on%20any%20non-public%2C%20material%20information.%20To%20the%20best%20of%20my%20knowledge%2C%20the%20views%20expressed%20in%20this%20Insight%20comply%20with%20Indian%20law%20as%20well%20as%20applicable%20law%20in%20the%20country%20from%20which%20it%20is%20posted.%20I%20have%20not%20been%20commissioned%20to%20write%20this%20Insight%20or%20hold%20any%20specific%20opinion%20on%20the%20securities%20referenced%20therein.%20This%20Insight%20is%20for%20informational%20purposes%20only%20and%20is%20not%20intended%20to%20provide%20financial%2C%20investment%20or%20other%20professional%20advice.%20It%20should%20not%20be%20construed%20as%20an%20offer%20to%20sell%2C%20a%20solicitation%20of%20an%20offer%20to%20buy%2C%20or%20a%20recommendation%20for%20any%20security.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20rights%20reserved.%20No%20portion%20of%20this%20article%20may%20be%20reproduced%20in%20any%20form%20without%20permission%20from%20the%20author.%20For%20permissions%20contact%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahkh%40hemindrahazari.com%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehkh%40hemindrahazari.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690810211000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Fthe-toxic-work-culture-in-the-financial-sector-is-a-reflection-of-deeper-concerns%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20toxic%20work%20culture%20is%20symptomatic%20of%20larger%20issues%20in%20the%20sector%2C%20such%20as%20setting%20unrealistic%20sales%20targets%2C%20poor%20leadership%20development%2C%20and%20lack%20of%20communication%20skills.%20These%20factors%20are%20not%20always%20publicly%20discussed%20by%20the%20senior%20management.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Fthe-toxic-work-culture-in-the-financial-sector-is-a-reflection-of-deeper-concerns%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Portable%20Innovation%20Saves%20Lives%20by%20Bringing%20Doctors%20to%2030%20Lakh%20Pregnant%20Women%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAntenatal%20care%20is%20designed%20to%20make%20pregnancy%20safer%20for%20women%20by%20detecting%20complications%20early%20and%20ensuring%20timely%20treatment.%20At%20least%20four%20antenatal%20care%20visits%20are%20recommended%20to%20monitor%20the%20health%20of%20the%20pregnant%20woman%20and%20her%20fetus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20rural%20areas%2C%20about%2054%20percent%20of%20mothers%20attend%20the%20recommended%20visits%2C%20compared%20to%2068.1%20percent%20in%20urban%20areas.%20This%20implies%20that%20roughly%20half%20of%20pregnant%20women%20in%20rural%20regions%20do%20not%20visit%20hospitals%20for%20advised%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20these%20complications%20significantly%20impact%20women%E2%80%99s%20lives.%20In%20India%2C%20there%20were%2097%20maternal%20deaths%20per%201%2C00%2C000%20live%20births%20reported%20between%202018%E2%80%9320.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20major%20reasons%20behind%20such%20deaths%20is%20that%20women%20avoid%20going%20to%20far-off%20healthcare%20centres%20for%20routine%20checkups.%20The%20complications%2C%20if%20any%2C%20remain%20ignored%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tamil%20Nadu-based%20Senthil%20Kumar%20Murugesan%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHigh-risk%20mothers%20are%20usually%20identified%20in%20the%20third%20trimester%2C%20which%20is%20around%20the%20eighth%20month%20of%20pregnancy.%20However%2C%20by%20this%20time%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20often%20too%20late%20to%20effectively%20manage%20complications%20before%20labour.%20This%20can%20lead%20to%20fatal%20outcomes.%20Currently%2C%20all%20records%20are%20maintained%20on%20paper%2C%20and%20if%20mortality%20occurs%2C%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20death%20remains%20unknown.%20There%20are%20no%20data-based%20analyses%20available%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2033-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw