%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-video-two-kuki-women-paraded-naked-gang-raped%5C%22%3Eplea%20filed%20by%20two%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Kuki%20community%20who%20were%20paraded%20naked%20by%20a%20mob%20of%20men%20on%20May%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20occurred%20in%20B.%20Phainom%20village%20in%20Kangpokpi%20district%2C%20one%20day%20after%20the%20ongoing%20ethnic%20clashes%20between%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20Kukis%20began.%20However%2C%20the%20video%20went%20viral%20only%20on%20July%2019%2C%20following%20which%20several%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpiyush-goyal-says-govt-will-discuss-manipur-in-parliament-at-2-pm-opposition-firm-on-modi-statement%5C%22%3Epoliticians%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fleaders-express-outrage-over-brutality-impunity-with-which-women-were-assaulted-in-manipur-violence%5C%22%3Eand%20groups%3C%2Fa%3E%20expressed%20outrage%20at%20the%20brutality%20and%20impunity%20with%20which%20the%20women%20were%20assaulted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-video-two-kuki-women-paraded-naked-gang-raped%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20top%20court%20was%20responding%20to%20advocate%20Bansuri%20Swaraj%E2%80%99s%20remark%20who%20highlighted%20that%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20mobs%20had%20paraded%20women%20naked.%20The%20advocate%20asked%20the%20top%20court%20to%20take%20up%20similar%20incidents%20from%20Bengal%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20gain%20saying%20the%20fact%20that%20crimes%20against%20women%20are%20taking%20place%20in%20all%20parts.%20The%20only%20answer%20is%20this.%20You%20cannot%20excuse%20what%20is%20taking%20place%20in%20one%20part%20of%20the%20country%2C%20like%20Manipur%2C%20on%20the%20ground%20%5Bby%20saying%5D%20that%20similar%20crimes%20are%20happening%20in%20other%20parts%20too.%20Question%20is%20how%20do%20we%20deal%20with%20Manipur.%20Mention%20that%E2%80%A6Are%20you%20saying%20protect%20all%20daughters%20of%20India%20or%20don%E2%80%99t%20protect%20anyone%3F%E2%80%9D%20the%20CJI%20asked%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-on-manipur-viral-video-manipur-women-paraded-naked-manipur-viral-video-incident-not-isolated-chief-justice-asks-how-many-firs-registered-4254901%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Kapil%20Sibal%2C%20representing%20the%20women%2C%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20data%20now%20to%20tell%20you%20how%20many%20such%20cases%20have%20been%20registered.%20That%20shows%20the%20state%20of%20affairs.%E2%80%9D%20He%20made%20these%20comments%20while%20requesting%20for%20a%20Supreme%20Court-monitored%20probe%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2020%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-takes-suo-motu-cognisance-of-viral-video-of-assaulted-women-in-manipur-seeks-action-from-government-101689880716815.html%5C%22%3Etook%3C%2Fa%3E%20suo%20motu%20cognisance%20of%20the%20sexual%20violence%20video%2C%20asking%20the%20government%20to%20take%20action%20or%20else%20it%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20give%20a%20little%20time%20for%20the%20government%20to%20take%20action%20otherwise%20we%20will%20step%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20CJI%20said%2C%20after%20asking%20details%20of%20the%20action%20taken%20by%20the%20authorities%20to%20book%20the%20criminals%20since%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20May%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20also%20asked%20the%20government%20whether%20this%20incident%20was%20isolated%20or%20a%20pattern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fthey-killed-my-husband-mother-in-law-smashed-my-head-says-29-year-old-kuki-survivor%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3E%E2%80%98They%20Killed%20My%20Husband%2C%20Mother-In-Law%2C%20Smashed%20My%20Head%2C%E2%80%99%20Says%2029-Year-Old%20Kuki%20Survivor%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20justice%20also%20questioned%20what%20did%20police%20do%20for%2014%20days%2C%20considering%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cincident%20came%20to%20light%20on%20May%204%E2%80%9D%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Flaw%2Fstory%2Fmanipur-viral-video-case-survivors-move-fresh-plea-in-supreme-court-2413947-2023-07-31%5C%22%3E%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20also%20asked%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20state%20government%20to%20give%20details%20about%20the%20first%20information%20reports%20(FIRs)%20filed%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20know%20the%20bifurcation%20of%206%2C000%20FIRs%2C%20how%20many%20zero%20FIRs%2C%20how%20many%20forwarded%20to%20jurisdictional%20magistrate%2C%20action%20taken%2C%20how%20many%20in%20judicial%20custody%2C%20how%20many%20involving%20sexual%20violence%20and%20position%20of%20the%20legal%20aid%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20CJI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20committee%20of%20women%20judges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20the%20top%20court%20contemplated%20formation%20of%20a%20committee%20of%20retired%20woman%20judges%20to%20probe%20incidents%20of%20sexual%20violence%20against%20women%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMerely%20entrusting%20to%20CBI%20or%20SIT%20(Special%20Investigation%20Team)%20would%20not%20be%20enough.%20We%20will%20have%20to%20picture%20a%20situation%20where%20a%2019-year-old%20woman%20who%20has%20lost%20her%20family%20is%20in%20a%20relief%20camp.%20We%20cannot%20have%20her%20going%20to%20the%20magistrate.%20We%20have%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20process%20of%20justice%20goes%20to%20her%20doorstep.%20We%20will%20constitute%20a%20committee%20of%20women%20judges%20and