0the%20board%20exams.%20But%20not%20Bhagyashree%20Bhansali.%20She%20went%20and%20joined%20the%202011%20anti-corruption%20movement%20launched%20by%20activist%20Anna%20Hazare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20devoted%20her%20college%20life%20to%20addressing%20public%20grievances.%20While%20pursuing%20her%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20in%20business%20administration%2C%20she%20joined%20the%20Delhi%20government%E2%80%99s%20advisory%20team.%20She%20focused%20on%20environmental%20issues%20such%20as%20air%20and%20water%20pollution%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323755%2Fmothers-anupama-charulatha-swmrt-bengaluru-plastic-free-low-waste-wedding-composting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emunicipal%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20biodiversity%20loss%2C%20which%20have%20been%20persistent%20challenges%20for%20the%20capital%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20work%20involved%20thinking%20of%20different%20ways%20to%20manage%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20waste%2C%20which%20led%20her%20to%20the%20Ghazipur%20landfill%2C%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20garbage%20dump%20yards%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20were%20facing%20health%20issues%20due%20to%20environmental%20pollution.%20We%20would%20make%20multiple%20visits%20to%20the%20Ghazipur%20landfill%20and%20seeing%20its%20condition%20just%20shook%20me.%20I%20was%20frustrated%20seeing%20the%20sheer%20number%20of%20plastic%20bottles%20and%20chip%20packets%20there%3B%20the%20amount%20of%20plastic%20waste%20there%20was%20humongous%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhagyashree%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20Ghazipur%20landfill%20has%2078%20lakh%20MT%20of%20waste%20and%20reached%20its%20saturation%20point%20in%202002.%20Yet%2C%20700%20MT%20of%20waste%20is%20dumped%20there%20daily.%20Work%20is%20underway%20by%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%20(MCD)%20to%20flatten%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20recycling%20her%20life%20mission%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201328px)%20100vw%2C%201328px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-11-min-1690546328.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221328%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Trash%20being%20separated%20in%20a%20dumpyard%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-11-min-1690546328.jpeg%201328w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-11-min-1690546328-300x168.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-11-min-1690546328-500x280.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-11-min-1690546328-768x431.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-11-min-1690546328-150x84.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325579%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22745%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETrash%20being%20separated%20in%20a%20dumpyard%20by%20TDC%E2%80%99s%20workers%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhagyashree%20interacted%20with%20rag%20pickers%20and%20waste%20segregators%20to%20understand%20what%20happens%20to%20plastic%20waste.%20%E2%80%9CBack%20then%2C%20most%20of%20the%20waste%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20recycled%3B%20it%20was%20just%20incinerated%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20adding%20that%20she%20was%20determined%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20weren%E2%80%99t%20a%20lot%20of%20recycling%20units%20then.%20While%20looking%20at%20options%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20plastic%20menace%2C%20I%20met%20someone%20who%20wanted%20to%20establish%20a%20recycling%20unit%20in%20Delhi.%20So%20I%20helped%20him%20set%20up%20the%20unit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20the%20process%20of%20setting%20up%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F319912%2Ftamil-nadu-father-son-duo-senthil-kumar-recycle-plastic-bottles-into-sustainable-clothes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecycling%20unit%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20Bhagyashree%20learnt%20a%20lot%20about%20plastic%20recycling.%20She%20went%20to%20various%20exhibitions%20to%20see%20the%20different%20recycling%20machines%20used%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMachines%20used%20in%20Germany%20and%20China%20would%20segregate%20the%20waste%2C%20but%20those%20machines%20could%20not%20process%20the%20type%20of%20waste%20we%20produced.%20So%20we%20had%20to%20segregate%20and%20clean%20the%20waste%20properly%20before%20using%20the%20machines%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2029-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20they%20set%20up%20small%20segregation%20systems%20and%20tweaked%20the%20machinery%20to%20work%20according%20to%20the%20waste%20they%20needed%20to%20recycle%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20college%2C%20she%20continued%20to%20work%20with%20local%20recyclers%20and%20partnered%20with%20organisations%20like%20Mohan%20Meakins%2C%20Whirlpool%2C%20and%20Arvind%20Mills%20to%20establish%20efficient%20in-house%20plastic%20waste%20management%20systems.%20%E2%80%9CI%20learnt%20how%20to%20identify%20different%20kinds%20of%20plastic%2C%20its%20nature%2C%20qualities%20and%20recyclability%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20these%20learnings%20which%20eventually%20led%20to%20her%20startup%2C%20The%20Disposal%20Company%20(TDC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELove%20for%20skincare%20turned%20into%20a%20business%20idea%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201113px)%20100vw%2C%201113p