n%20the%20packaging!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20time%20I%20see%20a%20new%20brand%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20that%20catches%20my%20eye%20is%20the%20packaging.%20Almost%20100%20new%20brands%20have%20come%20up%2C%20and%20most%20FMCG%20(fast-moving%20consumer%20goods)%20brands%20use%20low-value%20packaging.%20I%20was%20horrified%20at%20the%20waste%20we%20are%20accumulating%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20now%20Mumbai-based%20businesswoman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311038%2Fmani-vajipey-raj-madangopal-banyan-nation-hyderabad-recycle-plastic-waste-into-fmcg-bottles-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplastic%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E%20generated%20by%20so%20many%20new%20brands%20with%20new%20types%20of%20packaging%20gave%20her%20sleepless%20nights.%20This%20led%20her%20to%20start%20The%20Disposal%20Company%20in%20November%202020%20to%20%E2%80%9Creduce%20waste%2C%20revive%20lives%20and%20restore%20the%20ecological%20balance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20startup%20is%20a%20plastic%20credit%20platform%20that%20helps%20brands%20neutralise%20their%20plastic%20waste.%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCqdA8n1ISWi%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCqdA8n1ISWi%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%