s%20with%20rag%20pickers%20and%20waste%20segregators%20to%20retrieve%20plastic%20waste.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20provide%20training%20and%20support%20to%20improve%20waste%20workers%E2%80%99%20skills.%20We%20also%20give%20them%20proper%20safety%20gear.%20We%20have%20provided%20jobs%20to%20500%20such%20waste%20workers%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Bhagyashree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20TDC%20knows%20the%20amount%20of%20plastic%20waste%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20neutralised%2C%20they%20retrieve%20that%20much%20waste%20from%20the%20Ghazipur%20landfills%20with%20the%20help%20of%20rag%20pickers.%20Once%20retrieved%2C%20they%20segregate%20the%20plastic%20and%20send%20it%20to%20recyclers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETDC%20works%20with%20recycling%20companies%20like%20Thermowaste%20Solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20recycle%20plastic%20waste%20into%20granules.%20We%20sell%20these%20granules%20to%20companies%20who%20use%20them%20to%20make%20sustainable%20products%20like%20photo%20frames%2C%20toys%20etc.%20Mixed%20plastic%2C%20which%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20recycle%2C%20is%20sent%20to%20a%20plant%20that%20converts%20it%20to%20energy.%20We%20recycle%20about%2060%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20waste%20per%20month.%2020%E2%80%9325%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20credit%20is%20given%20to%20TDC%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Sanyam%20Jain%20of%20Thermowaste%20Solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20a%20better%20planet%20for%20the%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201196px)%20100vw%2C%201196px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-14-min-1690546327.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221196%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Waste%20being%20picked%20up%20by%20TDC%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-14-min-1690546327.jpeg%201196w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-14-min