0Lori%20Chauhan%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98The%20Corn%20Village%20Cafe%20%26amp%3B%20Bakery%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20first%20glance%2C%20the%20cafe%20would%20look%20like%20any%20other%20small%20tea%20shop%20with%20tables%20facing%20the%20picturesque%20hill%20views%2C%20serving%20tea%20and%20coffee%20to%20hungry%20travellers.%20However%2C%20if%20you%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20speak%20to%20its%20humble%20baker%2C%20Lori%20will%20tell%20you%20that%20although%20she%20enjoys%20sharing%20her%20love%20for%20baking%20with%20visitors%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20her%20only%20passion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20purpose%20behind%20running%20the%20cafe%20is%20to%20raise%20money%20to%20run%20the%20school%20she%20started%20for%20underprivileged%20children%20from%20nearby%20villages.%20Called%20Garhwal%20English%20Medium%20School%2C%20it%20currently%20provides%20education%20to%20around%20125%20children%20from%2025%20different%20villages%20in%20the%20Jounpur%20Block%20of%20Tehri%20Garhwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20proceeds%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F314772%2Funconventional-art-cafes-of-india-to-sing-play-doodle-paint-quiz-unique-workshops%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrom%20the%20cafe%3C%2Fa%3E%20go%20towards%20running%20the%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStayed%20back%20in%20India%20for%20love%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20a%20small%20town%20near%20Ontario%2C%20Canada%20with%20four%20sisters%20and%20a%20brother%2C%20it%20was%20from%20her%20mother%20that%20Lori%20learnt%20baking%20at%20the%20age%20of%20eight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCU1seNdpDns%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.