te-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClimbing%20Kilimanjaro%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20very%20difficult.%20The%20weather%20was%20extremely%20cold%2C%20and%20the%20food%20was%20very%20bad!%20It%20was%20taking%20me%20longer%20to%20eat%20it%20as%20it%20did%20not%20taste%20as%20good%20as%20my%20mother%E2%80%99s%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CI%20missed%20my%20mother%20a%20lot%2C%20but%20I%20was%20determined%20to%20keep%20going.%20I%20kept%20picturing%20how%20stunning%20the%20peak%20would%20be%20and%20looked%20forward%20to%20a%20big%20party%20at%20home%20once%20I%20returned.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20an%20average%20adult%2C%20it%20takes%20about%20seven%20to%20nine%20days%20to%20reach%20Mount%20Kilimanjaro%E2%80%99s%20summit%20and%20then%20descend%20to%20the%20finishing%20point.%20The%20trek%20is%20a%2064-km%20hike%20with%20the%20peak%20standing%20at%2019%2C340%20feet%20above%20sea%20level.%20Considered%20to%20be%20a%20moderately%20difficult%20climb%2C%20its%20low%20oxygen%20environment%20and%20low%20temperatures%20are%20both%20physically%20and%20mentally%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarsha%20elaborates%20on%20the%20challenges%20the%20duo%20faced%20on%20the%20climb.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20trek%20is%20fairly%20difficult%20even%20for%20an%20adult%2C%20and%20her%20tiny%20feet%20could%20not%20take%20long%20strides.%20So%20it%20took%20her%20longer%20than%20a%20full-grown%20adult%20to%20complete%20every%20day%E2%80%99s%20trek.%20We%20would%20trek%20for%2012%20hours%20straight%20with%20basic%20breaks%20for%20snacks%20and%20lunch%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20temperatures%20were%20very%20low%20and%20reached%20-20%20degrees%20Celsius%20on%20the%20summit%20night%20and%20she%20trekked%20for%2017%20and%20a%20half%20hours.%20Though%20she%20was%20wearing%20the%20best%20gear%20possible%2C%20her%20toes%20were%20numb%20with%20cold%20and%20the%20pain%20made%20her%20break%20down.%20She%20was%20very%20tired%20and%20wanted%20to%20go%20back%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCfOviKePfaV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCfOviKePfaV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCfOviKePfaV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Aadya%20Bennur%20(%40aadya.bennur)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20tried%20to%20encourage%20her%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20sun%20would%20make%20her%20feel%20better.%20It%20was%20tough%20because%20I%20could%20see%20her%20suffering%2C%20and%20I%20was%20torn%20between%20reaching%20the%20peak%20and%20comforting%20her%20by%20taking%20her%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20guides%20too%20recommended%20turning%20back%2C%20but%20then%20Aadya%20decided%20not%20to%20turn%20back%20and%20keep%20going.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAadya%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20says%20she%20kept%20herself%20going%20by