om%2F234151%2Fnew-education-policy-2020-pdf-hrd-ministry-play-school-classes-vocational-coding-bagless-information-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Education%20Policy%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20laid%20great%20emphasis%20on%20inclusion%20in%20education%20that%20takes%20into%20consideration%20local%20contexts%20and%20diversity.%20The%20framework%20asserts%20that%20quality%20in%20the%20early%20childhood%20care%20ecosystem%20(ECCE)%20is%20the%20highest%20priority%2C%20as%20is%20the%20inclusion%20and%20equal%20participation%20of%20children%20with%20disabilities%20and%20those%20from%20economically%20disadvantaged%20groups.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20how%20do%20we%20extend%20the%20same%20future%20benefits%20to%20children%20with%20disabilities%2C%20who%20are%20disproportionately%20affected%20by%20an%20already%20fractured%20educational%20system%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20first%20programmes%20that%20the%20Foundation%20started%20was%20Karuna%20Vihar%2C%20an%20early%20childhood%20intervention%20centre%20that%20encourages%20the%20overall%20development%20of%20children%20between%20the%20ages%20of%200%20and%206%20by%20building%20on%20their%20strengths.%20Parents%20or%20guardians%20work%20closely%20with%20special%20educators%20and%20therapists%20so%20they%20can%20carry%20out%20the%20activities%20practised%20during%20lessons%20at%20home.%20They%20are%20also%20given%20counselling%20services%20and%20support%20group%20interventions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaruna%20Vihar%20also%20focuses%20on%20%E2%80%98play%E2%80%99%20including%20theatre%20and%20creative%20interventions%20like%20exercises%20to%20help%20develop%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20functional%20skills.%20They%20also%20involve%20play%20in%20developing%20individualised%20education%20plans%20for%20each%20child%20to%20learn%20speech%20and%20language%20skills%20and%20alternative%20communication%20systems%2C%20as%20well%20as%20encourage%20sensory%20stimulation%20and%20behaviour%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20c