d%20with%20Anthill%20to%20build%20playgrounds%20in%20government%20schools%20in%20the%20past%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Central%20and%20State%20government%20are%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20policy%20focussing%20on%20early%20childhood%20development%2C%20of%20which%20play-based%20learning%20is%20an%20integral%20part.%20Building%20of%20structures%20like%20playgrounds%20with%20children%20playing%20in%20these%20spaces%20will%20facilitate%20their%20cognitive%20and%20behavioural%20development%20during%20early%20childhood.%20What%E2%80%99s%20also%20particularly%20encouraging%20is%20the%20minimal%20cost%20that%20went%20into%20building%20these%20playgrounds.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEducation%20should%20never%20be%20about%20textbook-based%20learning%20alone.%20The%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20the%20holistic%20development%20of%20children.%20Play%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20overall%20growth%20of%20a%20child.%20We%20have%20been%20mandated%20to%20focus%20on%20early%20childhood%20development%20(ECD)%20by%20the%20Union%20and%20State%20government%20because%20this%20is%20the%20time%20when%20children%20learn%20the%20most%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_171386959_474560363748134_6669212032293108365_n_1080-1689947152.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Innovate%20playgrounds%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_171386959_474560363748134_6669212032293108365_n_1080-1689947152.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_171386959_474560363748134_6669212032293108365_n_1080-1689947152-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_171386959_474560363748134_6669212032293108365_n_1080-1689947152-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_171386959_474560363748134_6669212032293108365_n_1080-1689947152-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_171386959_474560363748134_6669212032293108365_n_1080-1689947152-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324803%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22565%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20can%20be%20done%20to%20improve%20playground%20infrastructure%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20said%20that%2C%20in%20rural%20areas%20and%20in%20more%20remote%20geographies%2C%20Rai%20argues%20that%20we%20need%20more%20playgrounds.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20built%20playgrounds%20in%2023%20states%2C%20but%20not%20one%20in%20Bihar%20or%20Chhattisgarh%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20reasons.%20There%20is%20a%20big%20need%20for%20playgrounds%20in%20those%20states%2C%20but%20we%E2%80%99ve%20just%20not%20been%20able%20to%20raise%20funding%20to%20build%20playgrounds%20in%20those%20states.%20So%2C%20I%20think%20there%E2%80%99s%20an%20imbalance%20in%20where%20these%20playground%20resources%20are%20available%20and%20where%20the%20need%20is%20most%20urgent%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20you%20resolve%20this%20conundrum%3F%20Rai%20notes%20that%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20things%20that%20can%20be%20done%20is%20bringing%20the%20government%2C%20corporates%20and%20playground%20builders%20together.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20times%20we%20see%20there%20is%20funding%2C%20but%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20government%20support.%20At%20other%20places%2C%20we%20have%20government%20support%2C%20but%20do%20not%20have%20funds.%20Bringing%20all%20three%20parties%20together%20has%20been%20a%20challenge.%20There%20are%20occasions%20when%20the%20government%20has%20funding%2C%20and%20they%20just%20install%20a%20few%20plastic%20slides%2C%20which%20is%20okay%20but%20not%20good%20enough.%20They%20can%20bring%20in%20organisations%20like%20us%20who%20are%20building%20playgrounds%20at%20lower%20cost%20that%20are%20also%20more%20durable%20and%20help%20in%20children%E2%80%99s%20growth%20and%20learning.%20We%20must%20align%20different%20stakeholders%20to%20one%20common%20mission%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Rai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAccording%20to%20the%20All%20India%20School%20Education%20Survey%20conducted%20in%202016%2C%2062%25%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F267418%2Fgoa-government-school-robotics-coding-scheme-first-india-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egovernment%20schools%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India%20do%20not%20have%20playgrounds.%20Diving%20deeper%20into%20the%20data%2C%20we%20realised%20they%E2%80%99re%20just%20talking%20about%20open%20playgrounds.%20They%20weren%E2%80%99t%20even%20considering%20play%20infrastructure%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20this%20state%20of%20affairs%2C%20better%20collaboration%20between%20the%20government%2C%20corporations%20and%20playground%20builders%20will%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20addressing%20this%20lacunae.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FPlaygrounds-in-India--1689947635.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Urban%20and%20rural%20playgrounds%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FPlaygrounds-in-India--1689947635.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FPlaygrounds-in-India--1689947635-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FPlaygrounds-in-India--1689947635-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FPlaygrounds-in-India--1689947635-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FPlaygrounds-in-India--1689947635-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324815%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHow%20do%20you%20get%20more%20children%20to%20smile%20in%20school%3F%20The%20answer%20lies%20in%20improving%20the%20state%20of%20playground%20infrastructure%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERural%20versus%20urban%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%2060%25%20of%20playgrounds%20built%20by%20Anthill%20Creations%20are%20situated%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20despite%20their%20extensive%20work%20in%20major%20urban%20centres%20like%20Delhi%2C%20Bengaluru%20and%20Mumbai.%20And%20as%20expected%2C%20there%20are%20major%20differences%20in%20how%20playgrounds%20are%20built%20in%20urban%20versus%20rural%20areas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F71-6LBAVJa8%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26rel%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D0%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26color%3Dred%26controls%3D1%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20Pooja%20Rai%20explains%20these%20differences%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20%E2%80%9CIn%20terms%20of%20designs%2C%20when%20we%20do%20these%20activities%20with%20children%20and%20urban%20areas%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20responses%20we%20get%20are%20very%20different.%20In%20rural%20areas%2C%20people%20want%20play%20elements%20that%20speak%20to%20their%20sense%20of%20adventure%2C%20but%20also%20stories%20that%20they%20care%20about.%20So%2C%20you%20have%20play%20elements%20shaped%20like%20elephants%2C%20horses%2C%20and%20more%20nature-based%20play%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20build%20playgrounds%20in%20urban%20communities%2C%20children%20want%20toy%20elements%20resembling%20cars%20or%20computers%20in%20their%20playground.%20If%20we%20go%20and%20just%20put%20the%20same%20play%20elements%20in%20all%20of%20these%20geographies%2C%20we%20are%20not%20really%20contextualising%20play%20to%20their%20local%20contexts%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20In%20rural%20areas%2C%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20space%20as%20compared%20to%20urban%20areas%20where%20sometimes%20they%20see%20schools%2C%20which%20are%20just%20four%20storey%20buildings%20with%20no%20additional%20playground.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3)%20%E2%80%9CIn%20urban%20areas%2C%20children%20might%20have%20seen%20a%20playground%2C%20so%20they%20are%20more%20familiar%20with%20what%20to%20expect.%20In%20rural%20communities%2C%20I%20see%20children%20get%20so%20amazed%20when%20we%20build%20the%20playground.%20For%20instance%2C%20we%20had%20built%20a%20slide%20that%20basically%20included%20tires%20to%20climb%20and%20then%20a%20slide%2C%20and%20they%20used%20to%20call%20it%20Disney%20World.%20The%20appreciation%20for%20playgrounds%20is%20a%20lot%20higher%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20key%20challenges%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F147968%2Fahmedabad-childhood-initiative-kids-playgrounds%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20playgrounds%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20rural%20areas%20as%20compared%20to%20urban%20areas%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20%3Cstrong%3EFunding%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20are%20working%20in%20cities%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20more%20funding%20available%20in%20terms%20of%20CSR.%20A%20corporation%20would%20want%20to%20build%20something%20in%20the%20local%20vicinity%20so%20they%20can%20also%20kind%20of%20monitor%20and%20take%20care%20of%20it%20in%20the%20long%20term.%20In%20rural%20areas%2C%20the%20funding%20availability%20is%20lower%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20%3Cstrong%3ETransporting%20material%20to%20remote%20areas%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20playgrounds%20that%20we%20had%20built%20in%20Odisha%20did%20not%20even%20have%20electricity.%20We%20had%20to%20get%20generators%20to%20use%20power%20tools%20that%20we%20needed%20to%20build%20a%20playground.%20For%20one%20of%20the%20playgrounds%20we%20built%2C%20the%20team%20had%20to%20take%20tires%20through%20a%20boat%20because%20there%20was%20no%20road%20near%20the%20town%20of%20Baulakani%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201274px)%20100vw%2C%201274px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playground-5-1689948285.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221274%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Playgrounds%20in%20Odisha%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playground-5-1689948285.jpg%201274w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playground-5-1689948285-300x199.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playground-5-1689948285-500x331.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playground-5-1689948285-768x508.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playground-5-1689948285-150x99.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324828%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22843%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERetrieving%20play%20spaces%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChallenges%2C%20however%2C%20aren%E2%80%99t%20restricted%20to%20rural%20playgrounds.%20In%20urban%20centres%2C%20particularly%20the%20major%20metros%2C%20there%20is%20a%20serious%20paucity%20of%20space%20due%20to%20a%20variety%20of%20factors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20Bengaluru%2C%20for%20example.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.janaagraha.org%2Ffiles%2Fpublications%2FPARKS-PLAYGROUNDS-SCORE-OF-BENGALURU-2017.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJanaagraha%E2%80%99s%20survey%20(2017-18)%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20parks%20and%20playgrounds%20in%20the%20city%2C%20Bengaluru%20only%20has%20%E2%80%9C2.2%20sq.m%20of%20open%20space%20per%20person%2C%20which%20is%20significantly%20short%20of%20the%20recommended%2010-12%20sq.m%20by%20the%20URDPFI%20(Urban%20and%20Regional%20Development%20Plans%20Formulation%20and%20Implementation*)%20guidelines%20set%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Urban%20Development%20(MoUD)%2C%20India.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20playgrounds%2C%20only%2038%25%20of%20them%20across%20the%20city%20have%20play%20equipment%20or%20facilities%2C%20while%20only%201%25%20are%20equipped%20with%20drinking%20water%20facilities.%20Going%20further%2C%20nearly%20half%20the%20playgrounds%20in%20the%20city%20lack%20lighting%20facilities%2C%20while%20only%204%25%20of%20them%20have%20toilet%20facilities%20and%2070%25%20are%20suffering%20from%20litter%20and%20garbage%20piling%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Part%201%20of%20the%20article%2C%20Srikanth%20Viswanathan%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Janaagraha%20Centre%20for%20Citizenship%20and%20Democracy%2C%20noted%20that%20although%20the%20survey%20was%20taken%20in%202017%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthings%20haven%E2%80%99t%20changed%20much%20since%E2%80%9D.%20Given%20the%20circumstances%2C%20there%20have%20been%20episodes%20where%20communities%20were%20required%20to%20reclaim%20play%20spaces%20for%20their%20children.%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202015%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20former%20students%20of%20Round%20Table%20School%20in%20the%20Roopena%20Agrahara%20area%20of%20Bommanahalli%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20led%20by%20Pallavi%20S%20and%20Ranjith%20M%2C%20began%20the%20process%20of%20retrieving%20a%20playground%20in%20their%20neighbourhood%20that%20the%20government%20wanted%20to%20sell%20to%20private%20builders%20to%20build%20an%20apartment%20complex.%20These%20students%20held%20conversations%20with%20local%20community%20leaders%20and%20legislators%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20playground%20for%20the%20growth%20of%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20learning%20abilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20managed%20to%20persuade%20the%20local%20councillor%20and%20MLA%20to%20spend%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20of%20their%20own%20funds%20to%20upgrade%20and%20maintain%20the%20playground%20after%20inviting%20them%20to%20a%20few%20sessions%20of%20an%20After%20School%20Life%20Skills%20programme%20organised%20by%20Dream%20a%20Dream%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20non-profit.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20about%2015%20schools%20in%20the%20Bommanahalli%20neighbourhood%20share%20this%20playground.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20this%20was%20achieved%20thanks%20to%20people%20like%20Pallavi%20and%20Ranjith%2C%20who%20come%20from%20marginalised%20backgrounds.%20As%20children%2C%20Ranjith%20picked%20up%20rugby%20while%20Pallavi%20played%20football%20on%20the%20same%20ground%20under%20Dream%20a%20Dream%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98After%20School%20Life%20Skills%20Program%E2%80%99.%20Established%20in%201999%2C%20Dream%20a%20Dream%20is%20a%20well%20respected%20Bengaluru-based%20non-profit%20working%20in%20the%20space%20of%20education%20and%20youth%20development%20for%20children%20from%20marginalised%20circumstances.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20sport%2C%20they%20had%20also%20picked%20up%20life%20and%20leadership%20skills%20on%20this%20ground.%20Over%20time%2C%20however%2C%20as%20development%20work%20picked%20up%20in%20the%20area%2C%20a%20dispute%20over%20who%20owns%20the%20land%20began%20to%20take%20shape.%20The%20government%20also%20got%20involved%20in%20this%20dispute.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20it%20grew%20into%20a%20vacant%20piece%20of%20land%20where%20people%20would%20dump%20garbage.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrasekhar%20%E2%80%94%20who%20handles%20a%20team%20of%2028%20members%20in%20the%20After%20School%20Life%20Skills%20Programme%20for%20children%20from%20marginalised%20communities%20%E2%80%94%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20challenges%20we%20faced%20before%20opening%20our%20centre%20there%20was%20that%20it%20was%20occupied%20by%20a%20local%20politician.%20Ranjith%2C%20Pallavi%20and%20a%20couple%20of%20more%20products%20of%20our%20programme%20fought%20for%20that%20space%20and%20regained%20that%20public%20ground%20for%20children%20in%20their%20community.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Ranjith%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ground%20in%20question%20was%20under%20litigation%20between%20some%20private%20players%20and%20the%20government%2C%20and%20over%20time%2C%20had%20become%20a%20public%20dustbin%20of%20sorts%20filled%20with%20garbage%20and%20stones.%20The%20end%20result%20was%20that%20there%20was%20absolutely%20no%20space%20in%20the%20community%20for%20young%20people%20to%20play%20football%20or%20any%20other%20sport.%20Upon%20seeing%20this%20vacant%20ground%2C%20Pallavi%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20something.%20After%20all%2C%20there%20was%20no%20playground%20within%20a%20three%20kilometre%20radius%20of%20where%20we%20reside.%20So%2C%20we%20reached%20out%20to%20our%20community%20leaders%20asking%20them%20whether%20we%20can%20repair%20the%20ground%20and%20use%20it%20given%20that%20young%20people%20from%20the%20community%20have%20no%20space%20to%20play.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20approaching%20community%20leaders%2C%20they%20offered%20their%20support%20to%20clean%20up%20this%20ground.%20We%20also%20enlisted%20the%20support%20of%20the%20local%20councillor%20and%20MLA%20as%20well.%20Many%20people%20in%20our%20community%20got%20together%20to%20clean%20up%20the%20ground%20even%20though%20its%20legal%20status%20remains%20under%20a%20cloud.%20Today%2C%20we%20play%20different%20sports%20and%20organise%20a%20bunch%20of%20local%20tournaments%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20nearly%20a%20year%20of%20negotiations%2C%20the%20alleged%20owner%20agreed%20to%20convert%20that%20vacant%20plot%20of%20land%20into%20a%20community%20playground%20for%20children.%20It%20took%20three%20months%20to%20convert%20that%20vacant%20plot%20to%20a%20community%20playground.%20By%202018%2C%20the%20playground%20was%20open%20for%20children%20from%20the%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Dream%20a%20Dream%20runs%20their%20football%20programme%2C%20which%20falls%20under%20their%20After%20School%20Life%20Skills%20programme%2C%20on%20this%20playground.%20The%20moment%20when%20Ranjith%2C%20Pallavi%20and%20other%20former%20students%20rallied%20the%20community%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20have%20a%20playground%20for%20children%20was%20significant.%20After%20all%2C%20no%20one%20knows%20the%20value%20of%20play%20better%20than%20people%20like%20Ranjith.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGetting%20introduced%20to%20rugby%20literally%20changed%20his%20life.%20Ranjith%20today%20is%20a%20college%20graduate%20who%20works%20at%20Dream%20a%20Dream%20as%20an%20associate%20manager%2C%20plays%20rugby%20for%20the%20national%20team%20and%20even%20coaches%20the%20under-14%20and%20under-18%20national%20team%20in%20the%20sport.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuffice%20to%20say%2C%20this%20is%20what%20a%20playground%20did%20for%20Ranjith%E2%80%99s%20life.%20Without%20play%20spaces%20like%20these%2C%20children%20suffer%20in%20ways%20that%20impact%20their%20long-term%20growth%20and%20development.%20In%20many%20of%20our%20cities%2C%20these%20spaces%20are%20shrinking%20and%20much%20more%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20to%20build%20and%20retrieve%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20you%20come%20across%20any%20innovative%20ideas%20or%20construction%20executed%20in%20playgrounds%20in%20your%20city%3F%20We%E2%80%99d%20love%20to%20hear%20all%20about%20it.%20Send%20pictures%20and%20information%20about%20the%20playground%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aeditorial%40thebetterindia.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeditorial%40thebetterindia.com%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0with%20the%20subject%20line%20%E2%80%9CChildhood%20Dialogues%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20Anthill%20Creations)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690265185000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-21-1689947045.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D324772%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20previous%20article%2C%20we%20spoke%20to%20Anthill%20Creations%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20non-profit%2C%20about%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20build%20a%20playground%20that%20is%20safe%2C%20sustainable%20and%20inclusive.%20In%20the%20second%20part%2C%20we%20explore%20the%20importance%20of%20playgrounds%2C%20state%20of%20their%20infrastructure%20and%20reclaiming%20play%20spaces.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324772%2Fbuilding-playgrounds-for-children-india-play-based-learning-education-anthill-creations-infrastructure%2F%22%2C